sue%20Ma%E2%80%99am.%20We%20are%20not%20allowed%20any%20space%20to%20do%20anything.%20We%20had%20student%20union%20elections%20at%20the%20University%20and%20there%20was%20permanent%20curfew%20imposed%20on%20gatherings.%20We%20could%20do%20nothing.%20Jamal%20bhai%20is%20talking%20of%20the%20Jantar%20Mantar%20area%2C%20but%20even%20on%20campuses%20there%20is%20permanent%20curfew.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20a%20journalist%2C%20a%20student!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20are%20your%20exams%3F%E2%80%9D%20Tara%20asked%20with%20more%20confidence%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ll%20be%20writing%20competitive%20exams%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20Ma%E2%80%99am%2C%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20said.%20Jamal%20shrugged%20noncommittally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWell%20then%2C%20Habibi%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20think%20of%20a%20petition%20sooner%20rather%20than%20later.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20their%20goodbyes%2C%20and%20as%20Tara%20moved%20away%2C%20Jamal%20lunged%20at%20the%20urn%2C%20tilting%20it%20forward%20till%20it%20was%20level%20with%20the%20table.%20There%20was%20not%20even%20the%20thinnest%20stream%20of%20tea%20left.%20%E2%80%9CSee!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDoesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%2C%20Jamal%20bhai.%20We%20are%20not%20here%20to%20have%20tea.%20Come%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20go%20outside%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Ererhi%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20parking%20lot.%20He%20has%20the%20best%20tea%20and%20the%20best%20gossip.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20never%20going%20there.%20Students%20hang%20around%20having%20chai%20and%20mathri%20and%20the%20moment%20someone%20senior%20arrives%20they%20all%20conveniently%20leave.%20Last%20time%20I%20had%20to%20pay%20300%20rupees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20lit%20another%20cigarette%20as%20they%20stepped%20out%20of%20the%20Press%20Club.%20Just%20at%20the%20entrance%2C%20a%20posse%20of%20policemen%20sat%20on%20plastic%20chairs%2C%20sipping%20tea%2C%20scrolling%20through%20their%20mobile%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20organisers%20are%20serving%20them%20tea%2C%20but%20not%20us!%E2%80%9D%20even%20Habibi%20was%20offended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHave%20you%20taken%20down%20all%20the%20attendees%20names%3F%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20called%20out%20to%20the%20policemen%20provocatively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASI%20Achche%20Lal%20looked%20up%20and%20sighed.%20The%20intemperance%20of%20youth%2C%20he%20thought%20to%20himself.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20engage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAren%E2%80%99t%20you%20ashamed%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20this%20was%20a%20bit%20much.%20Achche%20Lal%20leapt%20to%20his%20feet%3A%20%E2%80%9CAren%E2%80%99t%20%3Cem%3Eyou%3C%2Fem%3E%20ashamed%3F%20Going%20from%20one%20protest%20to%20another%20%E2%80%93%20not%20doing%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20honest%20work.%20Andolan%20jeevi%2C%20activist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20students.%20I%20am%20preparing%20for%20my%20UPSC%20exams%2C%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSerious%20students%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20all%20this.%20You%20should%20sit%20at%20home%20and%20prepare.%20And%20as%20for%20him%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20I%20know%3F%20Even%20he%20started%20off%20claiming%20he%20was%20preparing%20for%20competition.%20Now%20look%20at%20him%20%E2%80%93%20all%20age%20limits%20have%20passed.%20Wastrel%2C%20lives%20off%20his%20poor%20retired%20father.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20light%20had%20turned%20even%20darker.%20Jamal%20felt%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20breathe.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20Umar%20Khalid%20a%20wastrel%3F%20Every%20day%20there%20are%20injustices%20meted%20out.%20Nobody%20speaks%20up.%20Some%20of%20us%20have%20to%20protest.%20They%20said%20just%20now%20that%20we%20are%20the%20real%20patriots%2C%20we%20are%20the%20last%20line%20of%20defence%20for%20this%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Awdhesh%20Rana%2C%20tall%20and%20strapping%20got%20up%20from%20his%20chair%2C%20and%20swung%20his%20lathi%20at%20the%20two%20men.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20want%20to%20be%20Umar%20Khalid%3F%20I%E2%80%99ll%20show%20you%20Umar%20Khalid.%20Not%20only%20is%20he%20a%20wastrel%2C%20he%20is%20Jihadi.%20Terrorists%2C%20leeches%20all!%20I%E2%80%99ll%20book%20you%20under%20UAPA%20just%20now%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20As%20profanities%20flew%20from%20Constable%20Rana%E2%80%99s%20mouth%2C%20Habib%20felt%20a%20sharp%20stinging%20slap%20on%20his%20face.%20His%20eyes%20welled%20up.%20Jamal%E2%80%99s%20face%20was%20red.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchche%20Lal%20was%20shouting%20in%20anger%2C%20%E2%80%9CGet%20arrested%20and%20send%20your%20parents%20crying%20to%20me%20for%20help.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Press%20Club%20servers%20rushed%20out%20and%20intervened.%20%E2%80%9CSecretary%20saheb%20is%20calling%20both%20of%20you%20inside.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20and%20Habib%20were%20met%20with%20very%20grim%20faces%20inside.%20The%20secretary%20was%20livid%20at%20the%20organisers%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20to%20find%20places%20for%20such%20events.%20Gandhi%20Foundation%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20give%20space%3B%20Jantar-Mantar%20is%20out%20of%20bounds.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20spaces%20left%2C%20and%20then%20these%20people%20create%20a%20tamasha.%20Why%20do%20you%20call%20such%20people%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisers%20glowered.%20Jamal%20and%20Habib%20looked%20down%20at%20their%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETara%20moved%20forward%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20quite%20unnecessary%2C%20Jamal%20and%20Habibi.%20Pointless.%20You%E2%80%99d%20get%20booked%20under%20the%20UAPA%20for%20assaulting%20police%20officers%20and%20then%20stay%20inside%20for%20months.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20hit%20Habibi.%20He%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20even%20said%20anything%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20must%20know%20that%20that%20is%20exactly%20how%20it%20works.%20They%20always%20pick%20on%20innocent%20bystanders.%20Wasn%E2%80%99t%20that%20your%20point%20today%20at