s%2Fastronomers-uncover-seismic-ripples-in-oldest-known-spiral-galaxy-with-almas-aid%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EALMA%20telescope%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20enabled%20them%20to%20scrutinize%20this%20ancient%20galaxy%20with%20significantly%20enhanced%20detail%2C%20according%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fphys.org%2Fnews%2F2023-12-astronomers-seismic-ripples-ancient-galactic.amp%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Phys.org%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpecifically%2C%20we%20were%20interested%20in%20how%20gas%20was%20moving%20into%20and%20throughout%20the%20galaxy%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Tsukui%20said.%20%26quot%3BGas%20is%20a%20key%20ingredient%20for%20forming%20stars%20and%20can%20give%20us%20important%20clues%20about%20how%20a%20galaxy%20is%20fueling%20its%20star%20formation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20instance%2C%20the%20researchers%20not%20only%20succeeded%20in%20recording%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20gas%20surrounding%20BRI%201335-0417%20but%20also%20unveiled%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20seismic%20wave%20groundbreaking%20discovery%20for%20this%20early%20type%20of%20galaxy.%20The%20findings%20have%20been%20published%20in%20the%20Monthly%20Notices%20of%20the%20Royal%20Astronomical%20Society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disk%20of%20the%20galaxy%2C%20characterized%20by%20a%20flattened%20assembly%20of%20rotating%20stars%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20dust%2C%20exhibits%20a%20motion%20reminiscent%20of%20ripples%20spreading%20on%20a%20pond%20following%20the%20impact%20of%20a%20thrown%20stone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20vertically%20oscillating%20motion%20of%20the%20disk%20is%20due%20to%20an%20external%20source%2C%20either%20from%20new%20gas%20streaming%20into%20the%20galaxy%20or%20by%20coming%20into%20contact%20with%20other%20smaller%20galaxies%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Tsukui%20said.%20%26quot%3BBoth%20possibilities%20would%20bombard%20the%20galaxy%20with%20new%20fuel%20for%20star%20formation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20our%20study%20revealed%20a%20bar-like%20structure%20in%20the%20disk.%20Galactic%20bars%20can%20disrupt%20gas%20and%20transport%20it%20towards%20the%20galaxy's%20center.%20The%20bar%20discovered%20in%20BRI%201335-0417%20is%20the%20most%20distant%20known%20structure%20of%20this%20kind.%20Together%2C%20these%20results%20show%20the%20dynamic%20growth%20of%20a%20young%20galaxy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20considerable%20distance%20of%20BRI%201335-0417%2C%20its%20light%20requires%20an%20extended%20duration%20to%20reach%20Earth.%20The%20images%20observed%20through%20a%20telescope%20today%20offer%20a%20glimpse%20into%20the%20galaxy's%20formative%20years%2C%20harking%20back%20to%20a%20time%20when%20the%20universe%20was%20merely%2010%25%20of%20its%20present%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarly%20galaxies%20have%20been%20found%20to%20form%20stars%20at%20a%20much%20faster%20rate%20than%20modern%20galaxies.%20This%20is%20true%20for%20BRI%201335-0417%2C%20which%2C%20despite%20having%20a%20similar%20mass%20to%20our%20Milky%20Way%2C%20forms%20stars%20at%20rate%20a%20few%20hundred%20times%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20co-author%20Associate%20Professor%20Emily%20Wisnioski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20understand%20how%20gas%20is%20supplied%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20this%20rapid%20rate%20of%20star%20formation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpiral%20structures%20are%20rare%20in%20the%20early%20universe%2C%20and%20exactly%20how%20they%20form%20also%20remains%20unknown.%20This%20study%20also%20gives%20us%20crucial%20information%20on%20the%20most%20likely%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20observe%20the%20galaxy's%20evolution%20directly%2C%20as%20our%20observations%20only%20give%20us%20a%20snapshot%2C%20computer%20simulations%20can%20help%20piece%20the%20story%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703477460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fe163r4ig_spiral-galaxy_625x300_25_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fastronomers-detect-seismic-ripples-in-oldest-known-spiral-galaxy-4737808%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BRI%201335-0417%2C%20aged%20over%2012%20billion%20years%2C%20stands%20as%20the%20oldest%20and%20most%20distant%20spiral%20galaxy%20identified%20in%20our%20universe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fastronomers-detect-seismic-ripples-in-oldest-known-spiral-galaxy-4737808%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fastronomers-detect-seismic-ripples-in-oldest-known-spiral-galaxy-4737808%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fastronomers-detect-seismic-ripples-in-oldest-known-spiral-galaxy-4737808%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jolly%20White-Haired%2C%20Bearded%20Man%3A%20What%20Are%20The%20Origins%20Of%20Santa%20Claus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWe're%20all%20familiar%20with%20the%20jolly%2C%20white-haired%20and%20bearded%20overweight%20man%20who%20sneaks%20down%20chimneys%20on%20Christmas%20Eve%20delivering%20presents%20to%20children.%20But%20where%20did%20this%20come%20from%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20roots%20in%20Christianity%2C%20the%20origins%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20beloved%20gift-giver%20transcend%20time%2C%20culture%20and%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20starts%20with%20St%20Nicholas%2C%20a%20man%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20fourth%20century.%20No%20credible%20historical%20sources%20can%20prove%20the%20facts%20of%20his%20life%2C%20but%20according%20to%20tradition%2C%20St%20Nicholas%20of%20Myra%2C%20later%20known%20as%20St%20Nicholas%20of%20Bari%2C%20lived%20during%20the%20reign%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Fbiography%2FConstantine-I-Roman-emperor%5C%22%3EEmperor%20Constantine%20the%20Great%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.au%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FIcons_and_Saints_of_the_Eastern_Orthodox%2FuODOkMgUZKYC%3Fhl%3Den%26gbpv%3D1%26dq%3DNicholas%2520born%2520in%2520Patara%252C%2520Lycia%2520in%2520Asia%2520Minor%26pg%3DPA308%26printsec%3Dfrontcover%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20tradition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20was%20born%20in%20Patara%2C%20a%20city%20in%20ancient%20Lycia%20in%20Asia%20Minor%2C%20part%20of%20what%20is%20now%20Turkey.%20Nicholas%2C%20who%20would%20later%20become%20the%20bishop%20of%20Myra%2C%20was%20known%20for%20his%20profound%20Christian%20faith%20and%20extraordinary%20compassion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20historical%20record%20does%20not%20provide%20detailed%20accounts%20of%20his%20life%2C%20tradition%20tells%20us%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.au%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FMedieval_Art_Architecture_and_Archaeolog%2FuFb7CwAAQBAJ%3Fhl%3Den%26gbpv%3D1%26dq%3Dst%2520nicholas%2520Palestine%2520and%2520Egypt%26pg%3DPA96%26printsec%3Dfrontcover%5C%22%3Ehe%20travelled%20to%20Palestine%20and%20Egypt%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20youth%2C%20further%20cultivating%20his%20deep%20spiritual%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENicholas%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.au%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FHow_Far_Have_We_Strayed%2FYiDi4GNpEHEC%3Fhl%3Den%26gbpv%3D1%26dq%3DNicholas%2520born%2520in%2520Patara%252C%2520Lycia%2520in%2520Asia%2520Minor%2520orphaned%26pg%3DPA215%26printsec%3Dfrontcover%5C%22%3Eorphaned%20when%20he%20was%20young%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20left%20with%20a%20substantial%20inheritance.%20He%20chose%20to%20use%20this%20wealth%20to%20help%20the%20needy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20most%20famous%20act%20of%20generosity%20was%20providing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stnicholascenter.org%2Fwho-is-st-nicholas%2Fstories-legends%2Ftraditional-stories%2Flife-of-nicholas%2Fthree-impoverished-maidens%5C%22%3Edowries%20for%20three%20impoverished%20sisters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20acts%20of%20generosity%20meant%20when%20he%20was%20recognised%20as%20a%20saint%2C%20he%20was%20acclaimed%20as%20the%20patron%20and%20protector%20of%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESt%20Nicholas%20Day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20Europe%2C%20the%20legacy%20of%20St%20Nicholas's%20charity%20and%20kindness%20sparked%20a%20variety%20of%20traditions%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Ftopic%2FSaint-Nicholas-Day%5C%22%3EDecember%206%3C%2Fa%3E%20becoming%20his%20feast%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20France%2C%20particularly%20in%20regions%20such%20as%20Alsace%20and%20Lorraine%2C%20children%20would%20leave%20their%20shoes%20out%20for%20St%20Nicholas%2C%20hoping%20to%20find%20them%20filled%20with%20chocolates%20and%20gifts%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20tradition%20was%20accompanied%20by%20parades%20in%20which%20a%20donkey%20would%20pass%20through%20town%20streets%2C%20laden%20with%20baskets%20of%20biscuits%20and%20sweets%20for%20the%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Central%20Europe%2C%20particularly%20in%20Alpine%20regions%2C%20St%20Nicholas%20Day%20tradition%20merged%20gradually%20with%20unique%20local%20customs%20when%20the%20non-Christian%20population%20adopted%20Christianity%20as%20their%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20St%20Nicholas%20not%20only%20rewarded%20well-behaved%20children%20with%20gifts%20but%20was%20also%20accompanied%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalgeographic.com%2Fhistory%2Farticle%2F131217-krampus-christmas-santa-devil%5C%22%3EKrampus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20fearsome%20figure%20who%20would%20%E2%80%9Cpunish%E2%80%9D%20those%20who%20had%20misbehaved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20tradition%20underscored%20the%20contrasting%20themes%20of%20reward%20and%20retribution%2C%20integral%20to%20the%20local%20folklore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20regions%20of%20Poland%2C%20the%20earlier%20traditions%20centred%20on%20a%20figure%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flamusdworski.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F12%2F17%2Fgwiazdor%2F%5C%22%3EGwiazdor%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20%E2%80%9CStar%20Man%E2%80%9D%20dressed%20in%20sheepskin%20and%20a%20fur%20cap%2C%20with%20his%20face%20hidden%20under%20a%20mask%20or%20smeared%20with%20soot%2C%20carried%20a%20bag%20of%20gifts%20and%20a%20rod%20for%20naughty%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20transformation%20into%20Santa%20Claus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20metamorphosis%20of%20St%20Nicholas%20into%20Santa%20Claus%20was%20a%20gradual%20process%20influenced%20by%20cultural%20and%20religious%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Germany%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%2017th%20century%2C%20the%20practice%20of%20gift-giving%20in%20the%20name%20of%20St%20Nicholas%20began%20to%20take%20root.%20The%20Dutch%20called%20him%20%E2%80%9CSinterklaas%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20term%20that%20would%20eventually%20evolve%20into%20the%20English%20colloquial%20%E2%80%9CSanta%20Claus%E2%80%9D.%20This%20transformation%20first%20occurred%20in%20Germany%20and%20later%20spread%20to%20other%20European%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tradition%20of%20St%20Nicholas%20was%20brought%20to%20North%20America%20in%20the%2017th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20various%20iterations%20of%20St%20Nicholas%20were%20emerging%20in%20English-speaking%20communities%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20literary%20mentions%20of%20this%20figure%20in%20the%20American%20context%20was%20in%20Washington%20Irving's%201809%20book%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gutenberg.org%2Ffiles%2F13042%2F13042-h%2F13042-h.htm%5C%22%3EKnickerbocker's%20History%20of%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20portrayed%20Nicholas%20flying%20in%20a%20wagon%2C%20delivering%20presents%20to%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20red%20Santa%20suit%20and%20all%20related%20apparel%2C%20so%20familiar%20to%20us%20today%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20the%20invention%20of%20modern-day%20marketing%20in%20the%20English-speaking%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20Europe%2C%20St%20Nicholas's%20outfit%20draws%20more%20on%20the%20traditional%20image%20of%20the%20saint%2C%20with%20clothes%20more%20closely%20resembling%20a%20bishop's%20religious%20attire%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20mitre%2C%20the%20tall%20headdress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Legacy%20of%20St%20Nicholas%20and%20Santa%20Claus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20centuries%20of%20transformation%2C%20the%20core%20values%20of%20St%20Nicholas%20%E2%80%93%20generosity%2C%20compassion%2C%20and%20the%20joy%20of%20giving%20%E2%80%93%20have%20remained%20intact%20in%20the%20figure%20of%20Santa%20Claus.%20He%20has%20gone%20from%20being%20a%20revered%20Christian%20saint%20to%20a%20beloved%20secular%20icon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20evolution%20reflects%20the%20dynamic%20interplay%20of%20religious%20tradition%20and%20popular%20folklore.%20English-speaking%20Santa%20Claus%2C%20with%20his%20North%20Pole%20workshop%2C%20flying%20reindeer%2C%20and%20elves%2C%20may%20seem%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20historical%20bishop%20of%20Myra.%20Yet%20he%20continues%20to%20embody%20the%20spirit%20of%20giving%20that%20characterised%20St%20Nicholas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20thanks%20to%20global%20marketing%20and%20commercialisation%2C%20Santa%20Claus%20transcends%20religious%20and%20cultural%20boundaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20his%20origin%2C%20rooted%20in%20the%20life%20of%20St%20Nicholas%2C%20enriches%20our%20understanding%20of%20Christmas%20and%20connects%20us%20to%20a%20tradition%20that%20spans%20centuries%20and%20continents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20reminds%20us%20that%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20these%20festivities%20lies%20a%20timeless%20message%3A%20the%20importance%20of%20kindness%2C%20generosity%2C%20and%20the%20spirit%20of%20giving.%3Cimg%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22no-referrer-when-downgrade%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F216361%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistr