ay%20from%20cricket%20following%20the%20loss%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20come%20back%20from%20this%20(loss%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20final)%20the%20first%20few%20days...my%20family%2C%20my%20friends%20kept%20me%20going%2C%20kept%20things%20pretty%20light%20around%20me%2C%20which%20was%20quite%20helpful.%20It%20wasn't%20easy%20to%20digest%2C%20but%20yeah%2C%20life%20moves%20on.%20You%20have%20to%20move%20on%20in%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20captain%20remarked%20on%20social%20media%20following%20the%20heartbreak%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%202023%20final%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hitman%20acknowledged%20the%20immense%20disappointment%20of%20falling%20short%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%2C%20an%20aspiration%20he%20held%20dear%20since%20his%20childhood.%20Sharma%20articulated%20his%20disappointment%20and%20appreciation%20for%20the%20team's%20efforts%20in%20a%20candid%20social%20media%20conversation.%20A%20Test%20series%20victory%20in%20South%20Africa%20would%20bring%20the%20joy%20back%20to%20fans%20across%20the%20nation%20and%20also%20Rohit%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20times%20I%20thought%20we%20did%20everything%20we%20could%20from%20our%20side%20if%20someone%20asked%20me%20what%20went%20wrong%20because%20we%20won%2010%20games%20and%20in%20those%2010%20games%2C%20yes%2C%20we%20made%20mistakes.%20But%20those%20mistakes%20happen%20in%20every%20game.%20You%20cannot%20have%20a%20perfect%20game.%20You%20can%20have%20a%20near-perfect%20game%20but%20never%20a%20perfect%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20expressed%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%20team's%20journey%20in%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disappointment%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20loss%20is%20still%20fresh%20and%20Sharma%20understands%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20upcoming%20challenge%20in%20South%20Africa.%20It's%20a%20chance%20not%20just%20to%20redefine%20India's%20legacy%20in%20Test%20cricket%20but%20also%20to%20heal%20the%20wounds%20of%20a%20recent%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20leading%20the%20charge%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20aims%20to%20steer%20his%20team%20past%20the%20hurdles%20that%20have%20historically%20hindered%20India's%20success.%20The%20task%20ahead%20is%20formidable%2C%20with%20pace-friendly%20conditions%20posing%20a%20challenge%20that%20Indian%20teams%20of%20previous%20eras%20have%20grappled%20with.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20game%20and%20better%20preparation%2C%20Sharma's%20team%20appears%20primed%20to%20confront%20this%20challenge%20head-on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impending%20Test%20series%20in%20South%20Africa%20is%20about%20redemption%20and%20an%20opportunity%20to%20heal%2C%20evolve%2C%20and%20script%20a%20new%20chapter%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Sharma%20articulated%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20pure%20love%20from%20the%20people%20that%20I%20met%20and%20it%20was%20wonderful%20to%20see%20that.%20So%2C%20you%20know%2C%20it%20gives%20you%20motivation%20to%20get%20back%20and%20start%20working%20again%20and%20look%20for%20another%20ultimate%20prize.%26quot%3B%20And%20for%20him%2C%20that%20ultimate%20prize%20may%20well%20be%20etching%20his%20name%20as%20the%20first%20Indian%20captain%20to%20conquer%20the%20South%20African%20Test%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703475660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fh643h64g_rohit-sharma-pc-bcci_625x300_22_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fsouth-africa-tests-perfect-opportunity-for-skipper-rohit-sharma-to-heal-world-cup-pain-4728368%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20has%20not%20played%20for%20India%20since%20losing%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20final%20against%20Australia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fso