er%20an%20anonymous%20tip-off%20that%20some%20of%20the%20passengers%20on%20board%20the%20plane%20were%20%26quot%3Bvictims%20of%20human%20trafficking%26quot%3B.%20Two%20men%20were%20detained%20for%20questioning%20by%20a%20specialised%20unit.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20France%20has%20obtained%20consular%20access%20and%20are%20assessing%20the%20situation.%20It%20said%20it%20is%20working%20with%20the%20French%20government%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20Indian%20passengers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20stranded%20passengers%20were%20provided%20makeshift%20beds%20and%20access%20to%20toilets%20and%20showers%2C%20besides%20meals%20and%20hot%20drinks%20at%20the%20Vatry%20airport%2C%20an%20official%20said.%20Ten%20Indian%20passengers%20had%20even%20applied%20for%20asylum%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20AFP.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20lawyer%20claiming%20that%20she%20represents%20the%20Legend%20Airlines%20said%20they%20believed%20it%20had%20done%20nothing%20wrong%2C%20committed%20no%20offence%20%26quot%3Band%20is%20at%20the%20disposal%20of%20the%20French%20authorities%26quot%3B.%20She%20said%20the%20airline%20will%20take%20legal%20action%20if%20charges%20are%20filed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703470500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fm7ec04i_vatry-airport_625x300_25_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findians-stuck-in-france-free-to-leave-today-grounded-plane-cleared-for-departure-4737247%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20plane%20carrying%20several%20Indian%20passengers%20detained%20near%20Paris%20due%20to%20suspected%20human%20trafficking%20is%20free%20to%20leave%20today%2C%20a%20French%20court%20ruled%20on%20Sunday.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20the%20plane%20will%20return%20to%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findians-stuck-in-france-free-to-leave-today-grounded-plane-cleared-for-departure-4737247%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findians-stuck-in-france-free-to-leave-today-grounded-plane-cleared-for-departure-4737247%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findians-stuck-in-france-free-to-leave-today-grounded-plane-cleared-for-departure-4737247%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Snub%20to%20Russia%2C%20Ukraine%20Moves%20Christmas%20Date%20To%20December%2025%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20Orthodox%20Christians%20attended%20services%20on%20Sunday%20as%20the%20country%20for%20the%20first%20time%20celebrated%20Christmas%20on%20December%2025%2C%20after%20the%20government%20changed%20the%20date%20from%20January%207%2C%20when%20most%20Orthodox%20believers%20celebrate%2C%20as%20a%20snub%20to%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20Ukrainians%20are%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20in%20a%20Christmas%20message%20released%20Sunday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20celebrate%20Christmas%20together.%20On%20the%20same%20date%2C%20as%20one%20big%20family%2C%20as%20one%20nation%2C%20as%20one%20united%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20southern%20Black%20Sea%20port%20of%20Odesa%2C%20churchgoers%20prayed%20and%20lit%20candles%20as%20priests%20in%20gold%20vestments%20held%20Christmas%20Eve%20service%20in%20the%20Cathedral%20of%20the%20Nativity%2C%20decorated%20with%20fir%20trees%20and%20a%20nativity%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20we%20really%20should%20celebrate%20Christmas%20with%20the%20whole%20world%2C%20far%20away%2C%20far%20away%20from%20Moscow.%20For%20me%20that's%20the%20new%20message%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20smiling%20parishioner%2C%20Olena%2C%20whose%20son%20is%20a%20medic%20on%20the%20front%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20want%20to%20celebrate%20in%20a%20new%20way.%20This%20is%20a%20holiday%20with%20the%20whole%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20our%20independent%20Ukraine.%20This%20is%20very%20important%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Abandon%20Russian%20heritage'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20eastern%20Christian%20churches%20use%20the%20Julian%20calendar%2C%20where%20Christmas%20falls%20on%20January%207%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20Gregorian%20calendar%20used%20in%20everyday%20life%20and%20by%20Western%20churches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20signed%20a%20law%20in%20July%20moving%20the%20celebration%20to%20December%2025%2C%20saying%20it%20allowed%20Ukrainians%20to%20%26quot%3Babandon%20the%20Russian%20heritage%20of%20imposing%20Christmas%20celebrations%20on%20January%207%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20date%20change%20is%20part%20of%20hastened%20moves%20since%20the%20invasion%20to%20remove%20traces%20of%20the%20Russian%20and%20Soviet%20empires.%20Other%20measures%20include%20renaming%20streets%20and%20removing%20monuments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Orthodox%20Church%20of%20Ukraine%20formally%20broke%20away%20from%20the%20Russian%20Orthodox%20Church%20over%20Moscow's%20annexation%20of%20Crimea%20in%202014%20and%20its%20support%20for%20separatists%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Join%20civilised%20world'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20rift%20has%20seen%20priests%20and%20even%20entire%20parishes%20swap%20from%20one%20church%20to%20another%2C%20with%20the%20new%20Orthodox%20Church%20of%20Ukraine%20growing%20fast%20and%20taking%20over%20several%20Russia-linked%20church%20buildings%2C%20moves%20supported%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20worshippers%20packed%20St%20Michael's%20Golden-Domed%20Monastery%20in%20Kyiv%20--%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20new%20independent%20church%20--%20for%20a%20Christmas%20service%20led%20by%20the%20primate%20of%20the%20Orthodox%20Church%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20Metropolitan%20Yepifaniy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainians%20around%20the%20country%20voiced%20support%20for%20the%20Christmas%20date%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20support%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Ukraine%20now.%20Because%20changes%20are%20always%20difficult%2C%20and%20when%20these%20changes%20occur%2C%20more%20people%20are%20needed%20to%20support%20it%20in%20order%20for%20something%20new%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Denis%2C%20a%20young%20man%20attending%20church%20in%20Odesa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Kyiv's%20Golden-Domed%20Monastery%2C%20Oksana%20Krykunova%20said%20that%20for%20her%2C%20after%20the%20invasion%2C%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bnatural%20to%20switch%20to%20the%2025th%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20visited%20my%20parents%20--%20my%2081-year-old%20mother%20and%2086-year-old%20father%20--%20and%20they%20accepted%20it%20absolutely%20(normally).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20western%20city%20of%20Lviv%2C%20which%20has%20been%20little%20damaged%20by%20the%20war%2C%20Taras%20Kobza%2C%20an%20army%20medic%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20to%20join%20the%20civilised%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETetiana%2C%20a%20singer%20in%20a%20traditional%20music%20group%20called%20Yagody%20(berries)%2C%20agreed%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20happy%20that%20we%20are%20finally%20celebrating%20Christmas%20Eve%20and%20Christmas%20together%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20It's%20really%20cool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20Greek%20Catholic%20Church%20has%20also%20opted%20to%20hold%20Christmas%20services%20on%20December%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20historically%20Russia-linked%20Ukrainian%20Orthodox%20Church%20is%20keeping%20the%20January%207%20Christmas%20date.%20This%20church%20claims%20to%20have%20cut%20ties%20with%20Russia%20because%20of%20the%20war%20but%20many%20Ukrainians%20are%20sceptical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20atheism%20was%20encouraged%20and%20Christmas%20traditions%20such%20as%20trees%20and%20gifts%20were%20shifted%20to%20New%20Year's%20Eve%2C%20which%20became%20the%20main%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20Christmas%20traditions%20include%20a%20dinner%20on%20Christmas%20Eve%20with%2012%20meatless%20dishes%20including%20a%20sweet%20grain%20pudding%20called%20kutya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20decorate%20homes%20with%20elaborate%20sheaves%20of%20wheat%20called%20didukh.%20Celebrations%20also%20include%20singing%20carols%20called%20kolyadky%2C%20carrying%20decorations%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20stars%20and%20performing%20nativity%20scenes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703470380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F59opjlho_ukraine-christmas_120x90_25_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-a-first-ukraine-celebrates-christmas-on-dec-25-to-be-far-away-from-moscow-4736528%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20Orthodox%20Christians%20attended%20services%20on%20Sunday%20as%20the%20country%20for%20the%20first%20time%20celebrated%20Christmas%20on%20December%2025%2C%20after%20the%20government%20changed%20the%20date%20from%20January%207%2C%20when%20most%20Orthodox%20believers%20celebrate%2C%20as%20a%20snub%20to%20Russia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-a-first-ukraine-celebrates-christmas-on-dec-25-to-be-far-away-from-moscow-4736528%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-a-first-ukraine-celebrates-christmas-on-dec-25-to-be-far-away-from-moscow-4736528%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.co