%2Fgadgets-news%2F53-year-old-bengaluru-techie-lost-rs-95-lakh-to-crypto-scam-what-it-is-and-how-to-avoid-one%2Farticleshow%2F106258559.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hrithik%20wishes%20Fighter%20co-star%20Anil%20on%20b'day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703470181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106258537%2Cimgsize-28376.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fhrithik-roshan-pens-a-sweet-birthday-note-for-his-fighter-co-star-anil-kapoor-calls-him-a-rocky-ing-human-see-photo%2Farticleshow%2F106258537.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106258537.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHrithik%20Roshan%20wishes%20Anil%20Kapoor%20on%20his%2067th%20birthday%20with%20a%20priceless%20throwback%20photo%20from%20the%20sets%20of%20'Khel'.%20Anil%20Kapoor's%20energy%20and%20mastery%20of%20craft%20remain%20incredible%20as%20ever.%20They%20will%20share%20the%20screen%20in%20the%20upcoming%20action%20drama%20'Fighter'.%20The%20film%2C%20directed%20by%20Siddharth%20Anand%2C%20is%20scheduled%20for%20a%20theatrical%20release%20on%20January%2025%2C%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20US-Canada%20Military%20Agency%20Has%20Been%20Tracking%20Santa%20Claus%20For%2068%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20US-Canadian%20military%20monitoring%20agency%20has%20continued%20its%20decades-long%20Christmas%20tradition%20of%20tracking%20Santa's%20whereabouts%2C%20helping%20children%20around%20the%20globe%20find%20out%20when%20his%20reindeer-powered%2C%20present-filled%20sleigh%20is%20coming%20to%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%203-D%2C%20interactive%20website%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.noradsanta.org%2Fen%2F%5C%22%3Ewww.noradsanta.org%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20Santa%20Claus%20and%20his%20reindeer%20on%20their%20imagined%20worldwide%20delivery%20route%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20click%20and%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20various%20cities%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Santa%20tracker%20presented%20by%20the%20North%20American%20Aerospace%20Defense%20Command%20(NORAD)%20dates%20to%201955%2C%20when%20a%20Colorado%20newspaper%20advertisement%20printed%20a%20phone%20number%20to%20connect%20children%20with%20Santa%20but%20mistakenly%20directed%20them%20to%20the%20hotline%20for%20the%20military%20nerve%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20disappointing%20the%20little%20ones%2C%20NORAD's%20director%20of%20operations%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Colonel%20Harry%20Shoup%2C%20ordered%20his%20staff%20to%20check%20the%20radar%20to%20see%20where%20Old%20Saint%20Nick%20might%20be%20and%20update%20the%20children%20on%20his%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESixty-eight%20years%20later%20NORAD%20is%20continuing%20the%20tradition%20of%20setting%20up%20a%20temporary%20call%20center%20out%20of%20its%20Colorado%20headquarters%20to%20answer%20children's%20burning%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20photo%20posted%20by%20the%20group%20on%20Facebook%20showed%20rows%20of%20people%20answering%20phones%2C%20some%20in%20uniform%20and%20others%20wearing%20red%20Santa%20caps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20top-level%20US%20dignitaries%20--%20namely%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20wife%20Jill%20Biden%20--%20joined%20in%20on%20the%20holiday%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20evening%2C%20the%20President%20and%20First%20Lady%20participated%20in%20the%20North%20American%20Aerospace%20Defense%20Command%20Santa%20tracking%20calls%20with%20children%20and%20families%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Sunday%20the%20tracker%20went%20down%20for%20a%20short%20while%2C%20leaving%20children%20in%20the%20Pacific%20region%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20his%20exact%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHey%20%23SantaTrackers!%20We%20may%20be%20having%20a%20couple%20of%20technical%20difficulties%20with%20our%20tracking%20map%2C%20but%20%23Santa%20is%20still%20flying!%20He%20is%20headed%20to%20Fiji%20next!%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20which%20runs%20the%20tracker%20said%20on%20their%20Facebook%20page%2C%20before%20announcing%20a%20fix%20one%20hour%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFather%20Christmas%20had%20begun%20his%20journey%20with%20an%20out-of-this-world%20first%20stop%2C%20according%20to%20NORAD%3A%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20orbiting%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reindeer-pulled%20sleigh%20was%20also%20seen%20traversing%20Israel%20as%20well%20as%20crossing%20over%20southern%20Gaza%2C%20crisscrossing%20Africa%2C%20and%20venturing%20southward%20to%20Palmer%20Station%2C%20a%20research%20facility%20in%20Antarctica.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanta%20then%20headed%20up%20through%20South%20America%2C%20bound%20for%20the%20United%20States%2C%20unloading%20approximately%20100%2C000%20gifts%20every%20second%20for%20about%204.9%20billion%20total%20presents%20as%20of%200130%20GMT%20Monday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20tracker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20not%20spreading%20holiday%20cheer%2C%20NORAD%20conducts%20aerospace%20and%20maritime%20control%20and%20warning%20operations%20--%20including%20monitoring%20for%20missile%20launches%20from%20North%20Korea%2C%20something%20that%20may%20be%20on%20Santa's%20mind%20this%20year%20as%20he%20passes%20over%2C%20with%20the%20most%20recent%20ICBM%20test%20just%20days%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703470080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-12%2Fur1a28k