a%2Famp_articleshow%2F106258330.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20flight%20carrying%20300%20people%20was%20grounded%20and%20sequestered%20for%204%20days%20as%20authorities%20looked%20into%20a%20human%20trafficking%20tip%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Charter%20plane%20at%20Vatry%20airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6588d892ab6f2ebb11f6b8ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20plane%20reported%20to%20carry%20some%20300%20Indian%20citizens%20parks%20at%20the%20Vatry%20airport%2C%20eastern%20France%2C%20Saturday%2C%20Dec.%2023%2C%202023%20in%20Vatry.%20About%20300%20Indian%20citizens%20heading%20to%20Central%20America%20were%20sequestered%20in%20a%20French%20airport%20for%20a%20third%20day%20Saturday%20because%20of%20an%20investigation%20into%20suspected%20human%20trafficking%2C%20authorities%20said.%20The%2015%20crew%20members%20of%20the%20Legend%20Airlines%20charter%20flight%20en%20route%20from%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20to%20Nicaragua%20were%20questioned%20and%20released%2C%20according%20to%20a%20lawyer%20for%20the%20small%20Romania-based%20airline.%20(AP%20Photo%2FChristophe%20Ena)%3Cp%3E(AP%20Photo%2FChristophe%20Ena)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20charter%20plane%20was%20grounded%20for%20four%20days%20in%20France%20for%20a%20human%20trafficking%20investigation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETwo%20passengers%20were%20detained%20as%20part%20of%20an%20investigation%20into%20suspected%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Fhub%2Fhuman-trafficking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehuman%20trafficking%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMost%20of%20the%20rest%20were%20allowed%20to%20go%20back%20to%20India%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20charter%20plane%20sequestered%20while%20carrying%20303%20Indians%20to%20Nicaragua%20was%20authorized%20Sunday%20to%20leave%20the%20French%20airport%20where%20it%20has%20been%20grounded%20for%20four%20days%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Ffrance-indians-human-trafficking-plane-grounded-9cb85e74512bed93e87b22b2be9062e5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehuman%20trafficking%20investigation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lawyer%20for%20the%20airline%20said%20the%20plane%20would%20take%20many%20of%20the%20stranded%20passengers%20back%20to%20India%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20authorities%20were%20working%20through%20Christmas%20Eve%20on%20formalities%20to%20allow%20some%20passengers%20to%20leave%20the%20small%20Vatry%20Airport%20in%20Champagne%20country%2C%20regional%20prosecutor%20Annick%20Browne%20told%20The%20Associated%20Press.%20All%20of%20the%20passengers%2C%20including%20a%2021-month-old%20child%2C%20had%20been%20stuck%20in%20the%20airport%20terminal%20since%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20passengers%20were%20detained%20as%20part%20of%20a%20special%20French%20investigation%20into%20suspected%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Fhub%2Fhuman-trafficking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehuman%20trafficking%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20an%20organized%20criminal%20group.%20Several%20others%20requested%20asylum%20in%20France%2C%20according%20to%20the%20local%20administration.%20Prosecutors%20said%2011%20passengers%20were%20unaccompanied%20minors%20who%20were%20put%20under%20special%20administrative%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Legend%20Airlines%20A340%20plane%20stopped%20Thursday%20for%20refueling%20in%20Vatry%20en%20route%20from%20Fujairah%20airport%20in%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20for%20Managua%2C%20Nicaragua%2C%20and%20was%20grounded%20by%20police%20based%20on%20an%20anonymous%20tip%20that%20it%20could%20be%20carrying%20trafficking%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20was%20requisitioned%20by%20police%20for%20days%2C%20and%20then%20turned%20into%20a%20makeshift%20courtroom%20Sunday%20as%20judges%2C%20lawyers%20and%20translators%20filled%20the%20terminal%20to%20carry%20out%20emergency%20hearings%20to%20determine%20whether%20to%20keep%20the%20Indians%20sequestered%20any%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hearings%20were%20halted%20midway%20because%20of%20a%20dispute%20over%20the%20procedure%20used%20to%20block%20the%20Indians%20in%20the%20airport%2C%20and%20a%20decision%20on%20next%20steps%20was%20expected%20overnight%2C%20the%20prosecutor%20said%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seizure%20order%20for%20the%20airliner%20was%20lifted%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20%26quot%3Bmakes%20it%20possible%20to%20contemplate%20the%20passengers%20in%20the%20waiting%20area%20being%20rerouted%2C%E2%80%B3%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20Marne%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20Civil%20Aviation%20Authority%20then%20set%20about%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20necessary%20permissions%20for%20the%20plane%20to%20take%20off%20once%20again%2C%20which%20should%20be%20in%20place%20%26quot%3Bno%20later%20than%20Monday%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20prefecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegend%20Airlines%20lawyer%20Liliana%20Bakayoko%20told%20AP%20that%20the%20company%20hoped%20the%20plane%20could%20head%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20India%2C%20on%20Monday%20''with%20as%20many%20passengers%20as%20possible.''%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20estimated%20around%20280%20passengers%20should%20be%20able%20to%20leave.%20The%20prosecutor%20and%20regional%20administration%20could%20not%20confirm%20an%20exact%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20officials%2C%20medics%20and%20volunteers%20installed%20cots%20and%20ensured%20regular%20meals%20and%20showers%20for%20those%20held%20in%20the%20airport.%20But%20lawyers%20at%20Sunday's%20hearings%20protested%20authorities'%20overall%20handling%20of%20the%20strange%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E''I'm%20surprised%20at%20how%20things%20unfolded%20in%20the%20waiting%20area.%20People%20should%20have%20been%20informed%20of%20their%20rights%2C%20and%20clearly%20that%20was%20not%20the%20case%2C''%20Francois%20Procureur%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Ch%C3%A2lons-en-Champagne%20Bar%20Association%2C%20told%20BFM%20television.%20He%20called%20the%20mass%2C%20hasty%20airport%20hearings%20''unprecedented.''%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForeigners%20can%20be%20held%20up%20to%20four%20days%20in%20a%20transit%20zone%20for%20police%20investigations%20in%20France%2C%20after%20which%20a%20special%20judge%20must%20rule%20on%20whether%20to%20extend%20that%20for%20eight%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20wouldn't%20comment%20on%20what%20kind%20of%20trafficking%20was%20alleged%2C%20or%20whether%20the%20passengers'%20ultimate%20destination%20was%20the%20U.S.%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20a%20surge%20in%20Indians%20crossing%20the%20Mexico-U.S.%20border%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2015%20crew%20members%20were%20questioned%20and%20released%20Saturday%2C%20Bakayoko%20said.%20She%20said%20the%20airline%20denied%20any%20role%20in%20possible%20human%20trafficking.%20A%20%26quot%3Bpartner%26quot%3B%20company%20that%20chartered%20the%20plane%20was%20responsible%20for%20verifying%20identification%20documents%20of%20each%20passenger%20and%20communicated%20their%20passport%20information%20to%20the%20airline%2048%20hours%20before%20the%20flight%2C%20Bakayoko%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20government%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Feurope-middle-east-human-trafficking-health-coronavirus-pandemic-4c35b8dbeb2085490180cc6f12534b38%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesignated%20Nicaragua%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20one%20of%20several%20countries%20deemed%20as%20failing%20to%20meet%20minimum%20standards%20for%20eliminating%20human%20trafficking.%20Nicaragua%20has%20also%20been%20used%20as%20a%20migratory%20springboard%20for%20people%20fleeing%20poverty%20or%20conflict%20because%20of%20relaxed%20or%20visa-free%20entry%20requirements%20for%20some%20countries.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fhaiti-nicaragua-charter-flights-migrants-89b54c6a42cae289c6488aa57f10d5e5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESometimes%20charter%20flights%20are%20used%20for%20the%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndian%20citizens%20were%20arrested%2041%2C770%20times%20entering%20the%20U.S.%20illegally%20from%20Mexico%20in%20the%20U.S.%20government's%20budget%20year%20that%20ended%20Sept.%2030%2C%20more%20than%20double%20from%2018%2C308%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-headed-to-nicaragua-investigated-for-human-trafficking-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703468457000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6588dc54ab6f2ebb11f6b8bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-headed-to-nicaragua-investigated-for-human-trafficking-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20flight%20from%20India%20to%20Nicaragua%20was%20grounded%20by%20police%20based%20on%20an%20anonymous%20tip%20that%20it%20could%20be%20carrying%20trafficking%20victims.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Insider%20Inc.)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-headed-to-nicaragua-investigated-for-human-trafficking-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Serbia%20protests%3A%20Anti-government%20demonstrators%20try%20to%20storm%20Belgrade%20city%20hall%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703468052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FE97D%2Fproduction%2F_132137795_7bf252c5582bb5df18ac5b0055223a2d787ec4d7.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-67817072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20opposition%20demands%20a%20re-run%20of%20last%20week's%20elections%20won%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20claiming%20mass%20fraud.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22en