%26quot%3BTonight%2C%20our%20hearts%20are%20in%20Bethlehem%2C%20where%20the%20Prince%20of%20Peace%20is%20once%20more%20rejected%20by%20the%20futile%20logic%20of%20war%2C%20by%20the%20clash%20of%20arms%20that%20even%20today%20prevents%20him%20from%20finding%20room%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Catholic%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20earlier%20stressed%20the%20%26quot%3Bcritical%20need%26quot%3B%20to%20protect%20civilians%2C%20in%20a%20call%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20who%20vowed%20Israel%20would%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20the%20war%20until%20all%20of%20its%20goals%20have%20been%20achieved%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20official%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20heavy%20fighting%20raged%20on%2C%20the%20Israeli%20army%20said%20154%20troops%20had%20died%20in%20Gaza%20since%20it%20launched%20its%20ground%20invasion%20on%20October%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETen%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20battles%20on%20Saturday%2C%20one%20of%20the%20deadliest%20days%20for%20the%20Israeli%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20war%20is%20exacting%20a%20very%20heavy%20price...%20but%20we%20have%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20keep%20fighting%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Christmas%20'cancelled'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20broke%20out%20when%20Hamas%20fighters%20attacked%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20and%20killed%20about%201%2C140%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20and%20seized%20250%20hostages%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20based%20on%20Israeli%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20withering%20military%20campaign%2C%20including%20massive%20aerial%20bombardment%2C%20has%20killed%2020%2C424%20people%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%2C%20according%20to%20Gaza's%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20said%20soldiers%20had%20raided%20a%20northern%20Gaza%20compound%20near%20schools%2C%20a%20mosque%20and%20a%20