fting%20Hijab%20Ban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20hijab%20issue%20continuously%20heating%20with%20each%20passing%20day%2C%20Karnataka%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20has%20said%20that%20the%20government%20will%20take%20a%20decision%20after%20looking%20into%20the%20matter%20deeply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20made%20any%20orders%20regarding%20hijab.%20CM%20Siddaramaiah%20himself%20said%20that%20even%20if%20it%20is%20done%2C%20we%20will%20check%20it.%20The%20government%20will%20take%20a%20decision%20after%20looking%20into%20it%20deeply%2C%26quot%3B%20G%20Parameshwara%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20leader%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20slammed%20the%20Congress-led%20Karnataka%20government%20on%20Sunday%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20has%20not%20lifted%20the%20ban%20on%20hijab%20yet%20in%20the%20state%20and%20they%20are%20still%20thinking%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20not%20lifted%20the%20ban%20on%20hijab%20yet%20and%20the%20CM%20has%20said%20that%20they%20are%20thinking%20about%20it.%20People%20are%20seeing%20the%20behaviour%20of%20Congress--what%20they%20say%20before%20coming%20to%20power%20and%20how%20they%20change%20after%20getting%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20KTR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20on%20the%20hijab%20issue%20again%20rose%20to%20prominence%20after%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20announced%20in%20a%20public%20meeting%20that%20his%20government%20would%20lift%20the%20ban%20on%20hijab%20imposed%20by%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20thinking%20of%20withdrawing%20the%20decision%20(of%20hijab%20ban).%20We%20will%20discuss%20it.%20I%20have%20said%20this%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question.%20We%20have%20not%20done%20it%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Minister%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20