0against%20unidentified%20persons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Mehmood%20Ahmed%2C%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20identified%20Shabbir%20and%20Showkat%20from%20the%20viral%20video%2C%20in%20which%20soldiers%20can%20be%20seen%20brutally%20beating%20the%20captive%20men%20and%20throwing%20chilli%20powder%20on%20to%20the%20bare%20buttocks%20of%20some%20of%20them%20%E2%80%93%20a%20common%20method%20of%20torture%20by%20the%20police%20and%20security%20forces%20across%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMohammad%20Siddique%2C%20uncle%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMohammad%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EShowkat%2C%20one%20of%20three%20civilians%20allegedly%20killed%20in%20Army%20custody%2C%20said%20that%20it%20was%20his%20nephew%20who%20was%20seen%20in%20the%20video%2C%20begging%20a%20lathi-wielding%20soldier%20with%20folded%20hands%20to%20let%20him%20go.%20%E2%80%9CShowkat%20begged%20for%20mercy%2C%20he%20pleaded%20to%20them%20with%20our%20Prophet%20Mohammed%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20but%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20melt%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddique%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20lifeless%20person%20in%20black%20clothing%2C%20also%20seen%20in%20the%20now%20widely%20circulated%20video%2C%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fanger-in-poonch-after-videos-show-three-dead-after-alleged-army-questioning%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESafeer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20whose%20brother%20is%20a%20head%20constable%20in%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cvideo%20width%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%20controls%3D%5C%22controls%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Csource%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fshorts%2F-YflgHiF6dA%3Fsi%3D2ZAinWTKhWgtsAL3%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fvideo%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20third%2C%20who%20is%20wearing%20a%20red%20t-shirt%2C%20is%20Irfan%20Ahmad.%20He%20is%2016%20years%20old%20and%20among%20those%20admitted%20to%20hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddique%20said.%20He%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20whole%20incident%20has%20sent%20shock%20waves%20through%20the%20Gujjar-Bakarwal%20community%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20which%20already%20battles%20poverty%20and%20a%20crippling%20lack%20of%20rights%2C%20among%20other%20problems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPoonch%E2%80%99s%20Topa%20Peer%20village%20has%20been%20locked%20out%20of%20the%20world%2C%20virtually%20sealed%2C%20thick%20with%20military%20presence%2C%20and%20under%20an%20internet%20shutdown%20since%20the%20bodies%20of%20those%20who%20had%20allegedly%20been%20tortured%20by%20soldiers%20from%2048%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20their%20families.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarpanch%20Ahmed%20also%20claimed%20that%20villagers%20are%20unable%20to%20visit%20the%20three%20families%20in%20their%20hour%20of%20grief%20because%20the%20army%20has%20cordoned%20off%20their%20homes.%20He%20also%20confirmed%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20and%20heavy%20army%20presence%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWali%20Mohammed%2C%20father%20of%20deceased%20civilian%20Mohammed%20Shabbir%2C%20says%20he%20has%20been%20drifting%20in%20and%20out%20of%20consciousness%20since%20he%20saw%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20dead%20body.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20turned%20my%20beautiful%20son%20into%20a%20body%20with%20stitches%20everywhere.%20I%20am%2060%2C%20I%20saw%20my%2027-year-old%20son%20barely%20held%20together%20because%20of%20stitches%20all%20over%20his%20body.%20Even%20his%20head%20and%20chest%20had%20stitches%2C%20his%20body%20had%20marks%20of%20electrocution%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohammed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMohammed%20said%20he%20himself%20had%20worked%20as%20a%20porter%20with%2027%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20as%20well%20as%2016%20Rashtriya%20Rifles.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20Shabbir%20was%20also%20a%20porter%20with%20the%20Army%2C%20why%20would%20they%20call%20their%20own%20employee%20in%20for%20questioning%3F%20They%20made%20it%20seem%20so%20normal%2C%20they%20phoned%20him%20up%20to%20come%20to%20the%20camp%E2%80%9D%20lamented%20Mohammed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20just%20worked%20with%20them%20but%20also%20stood%20by%20them%20on%20this%20uncertain%20border%2C%20this%20is%20our%20reward%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Mohammed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Army%20has%20said%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20matter%20is%20under%20investigation%20and%20that%20it%20stands%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fadgpi%2Fstatus%2F1738548583769759899%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecommitted%20to%20extending%20full%20support%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20cooperation%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20investigations%E2%80%9D%2C%20locals%20believe%20the%20bond%20between%20them%20and%20the%20Army%20will%20take%20a%20long%20time%20to%20rebuild.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ET%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20has%20not%20specified%20the%20cause%20of%20their%20deaths%2C%20but%20has%20said%20legal%20action%20had%20been%20initiated%20and%20compensation%20announced.%20On%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Information%20and%20Public%20Relations%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FJKCDC_%2Fstatus%2F1738762558688075973%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20death%20of%20three%20civilians%20was%20reported%20yesterday%20in%20Baffliaz%20of%20Poonch%20District.%20The%20medico%20legal%20formalities%20were%20conducted%20and%20legal%20action%20in%20this%20matter%20has%20been%20initiated%20by%20the%20appropriate%20authority.%20Government%20has%20announced%20compensation%20for%20each%20of%20the%20deceased.%20Further%20Government%20also%20announced%20compassionate%20appointments%20to%20the%20next%20of%20kin%20of%20each%20deceased.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKillings%20condemned%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20asking%20for%20a%20transparent%20inquiry%20and%20punishment%20for%20any%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%20seems%20pointless%20given%20how%20those%20who%20are%20found%20guilty%20are%20released%20scot-free%20without%20serving%20their%20punishment.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20way%20to%20remove%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fwant-to-remove-dilli-ki-duri-and-dil-ki-duri-pm-modi-to-jammu-and-kashmir-leaders-101624545589901.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edil%20ki%20doori%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20Dilli%20se%20doori%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20National%20Conference%20leader%20Omar%20Abdullah%20in%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20recent%20release%20of%20an%20Army%20captain%20convicted%20of%20killing%20three%20men%20in%20a%20staged%20gunfight%20in%20southern%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Shopian%20district%20in%20July%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPDP%20leader%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20has%20also%20condemned%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20three%20men%20Poonch.%20%E2%80%9CHad%20this%20happened%20under%20any%20other%20government%2C%20the%20godi%20media%20would%20have%20raised%20questions%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FMehboobaMufti%2Fstatus%2F1738553603089215771%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20said%20in%20a%20tweet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20picked%20up%2015%20people%20from%20their%20homes%20who%20were%20tortured.%20Three%20of%20them%20have%20already%20been%20killed.%20So%2C%20how%20is%20this%20%E2%80%98Khushal%20Kashmir%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98Naya%20Kashmir%E2%80%99%20where%20neither%20Armymen%20nor%20commo