20media.%20During%20the%20side's%20Big%20Bash%20League%20(BBL)%20match%20against%20Sydney%20Thunder%20in%20Albury%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Rauf%20came%20out%20to%20bat%20without%20his%20pads.%20The%20Stars%20lost%20three%20wickets%20in%20three%20consecutive%20balls%20in%20the%20last%20over%20of%20their%20innings%20and%20this%20caught%20Rauf%20off%20guard%20as%20he%20was%20not%20ready%20to%20bat.%20The%20player%20carried%20gloves%20and%20helmet%20with%20himself%20while%20entering%20the%20ground%20in%20a%20hurry%20but%20did%20not%20wear%20his%20pads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENo%20gloves%2C%20pads%20or%20helmet%20on%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHaris%20Rauf%20was%20caught%20by%20surprise%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Stars%20innings!%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKFCAustralia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40KFCAustralia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FBucketMoment%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23BucketMoment%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FBBL13%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23BBL13%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FZR9DeP8YhW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FZR9DeP8YhW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20KFC%20Big%20Bash%20League%20(%40BBL)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBBL%2Fstatus%2F1738445971972096196%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Rauf%20did%20not%20have%20to%20face%20any%20delivery%20as%20there%20was%20only%20one%20ball%20left%20in%20the%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20game%2C%20Melbourne%20Stars%20lost%20by%205%20wickets.%20They%20posted%20172%20all%20out%20in%2020%20overs%20after%20opting%20to%20bat%20first.%20Sydney%20Thunder%20cha