e%20an%20apartheid%20system.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20change.%20Because%20the%20entire%20system%20is%20controlled%20by%20a%20very%20thin%20group%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%2C%20along%20with%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20has%20been%20demanding%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census.%20In%20the%20recently%20concluded%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20promised%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20its%20manifestos.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20however%2C%20only%20won%20in%20Telangana%20and%20was%20voted%20out%20of%20power%20in%20the%20three%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-has-no-option-but-to-recover-in-heartland-states-in-2024%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHindi%20heartland%20states%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20conduct%20such%20a%20survey%20if%20it%20is%20voted%20to%20power%20in%20the%20general%20election%20in%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhy-the-bjp-is-afraid-of-a-caste-census%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20BJP%20Is%20Afraid%20of%20a%20Caste%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20earlier%20pressed%20for%20the%20need%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20saying%20that%20it%20reveals%20the%20composition%20of%20OBC%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20communities%20in%20the%20country%20which%20will%20will%20open%20up%20a%20window%20for%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fcongress-state-governments-caste-and-socio-economic-surveys-cwc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cnew%20development%20paradigm%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20government%20was%20attempting%20to%20turn%20India%20into%20a%20nation%20with%20%E2%80%9Cone%20ideology%2C%20one%20religion%20and%20one%20language.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20they%20kill%20the%20negotiation%2C%20they%20try%20to%20capture%20the%20institutions.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20really%20the%20political%20fight%20in%20India%20right%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20feel%20if%20you%20end%20the%20negotiation%20in%20India%2C%20the%20conversation%20between%20the%20union%20India%20collapses%2C%20India%20tears%20itself%20apart.So%20you%20can%20see%20that%20Manipur%20is%20burning%2C%20you%20can%20see%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20burning.%20You%20can%20see%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20a%20problem.%20As%20somebody%20said%20to%20me%20the%20other%20day%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20problem%20on%20the%20edges.%20And%20if%20you%20want%20to%20understand%20a%20system%20you%20got%20to%20look%20at%20the%20edges%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20scale%20civil%20war%E2%80%9D%20is%20underway%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20economic%20inequality%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20economic%20development%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmassively%20concentrating%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20talk%20about%20economic%20development%20you%20have%20to%20ask%20the%20question%20in%20whose%20interest%20is%20that%20economic%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRight%20next%20to%20the%20figure%20of%20growth%20in%20India%2C%20you%20have%20the%20figure%20of%20unemployment%20in%20India.%20So%20India%E2%80%99s%20growing%2C%20but%20the%20way%20it%E2%80%99s%20growing%20is%20by%20massively%20concentrating%20wealth%20towards%20very%20few%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EEconomic%20growth%20without%20meaningful%20employment%20fosters%20inequality%20and%20undermines%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20only%20a%20few%20close%20wealthy%20friends%20of%20the%20government%20are%20benefiting%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20economic%20growth%2C%20leaving%20common%20Indians%20grappling%20with%20unemployment%20and%20price%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEyHC1SpmwI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FEyHC1SpmwI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20(%40RahulGandhi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%2Fstatus%2F1738833537082802422%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2024%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimilar%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20we%20are%20operating%20on%20a%20debt%20sort%20of%20model%20and%20we%20are%20no%20longer%20producing.%20The%20real%20challenge%20in%20India%20is%20how%20do%20we%20set%20up%20a%20production%20economy%20that%20is%20able%20to%20give%20large%20numbers%20of%20people%20jobs.%20We%20have%20two%20or%20three%20businesses%20that%20are%20pretty%20much%20entire%20business%20system.%20We%20have%20Mr%20%5BGautam%5D%20Adani%2C%20everybody%20knows%20he%20is%20directly%20connected%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20he%20owns%20all%20our%20ports%2C%20airports%2C%20our%20infrastructure.%20With%20that%20kind%20of%20concentration%2C%20you%20will%20get%20growth%20but%20you%20will%20not%20get%20any%20distribution.%20And%20a%20country%20like%20India%20needs%20distribution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20why%20these%20inequalities%20are%20not%20reflecting%20in%20electoral%20outcomes%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20there%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmassive%20mobilisation%E2%80%9D%20but%20there%20is%20a%20requirement%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinfrastructure%20to%20fight%20an%20election%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20a%20fair%20media%2C%20fair%20legal%20system%2C%20fair%20election%20commission%2C%20access%20to%20finance%2C%20institutions%20that%20are%20neutral.%20Imagine%20a%20United%20States%20where%20the%20IRS%2C%20the%20FBI%2C%20their%20full%20time%20job%20is%20destroying%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20opposition.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20paradigm%20we%E2%80%99re%20in.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20walk%204%2C000%20kilometres%20because%20I%20like%20walking%204%2C000%20kilometres.%20I%20walked%204%2C000%20kilometres%20because%20there%20was%20no%20other%20way%20to%20get%20our%20message%20across.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20my%20social%20media%20is%20fully%20capped.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20got%20a%20shadow%20ban%2024%2F7.%20My%20Twitter%E2%80%99s%20under%20control%2C%20my%20YouTube%20is%20under%20control%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20alone%2C%20the%20entire%20opposition.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20India%20is%20running%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20democracy%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703416344000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01122618%2FF8oQIiNXkAA_m-k.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-trying-to-change-caste-apartheid-system-in-india-not-a-free-democracy-anymore%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20also%20said%20that%20economic%20development%20is%20%26quot%3Bmassively%20concentrating%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-trying-to-change-caste-apartheid-system-in-india-not-a-free-democracy-anymore%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Christmas%20Amidst%20Genocide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24161457%2FScreenshot-2023-12-24-at-4.09.24.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristians%20around%20the%20world%20will%20celebrate%20Christmas%20tomorrow.%20They%20will%20do%20so%20with%20accustomed%20joyousness%20and%20euphoria.%20But%2C%20they%20would%20generally%20be%20unaware%20of%20and%2For%20indifferent%20to%20the%20ongoing%20genocide%20and%20torturous%20everyday%20existence%20of%20people%20in%20Gaza%20under%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ruthless%20military%20tactics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EComfortable%20Christians%20and%20church%20bodies%20around%20the%20world%20function%20as%20if%20Gaza%20exists%20in%20an%20alien%20world.%20They%20might%20know%20partial%20facts%20from%20random%20glances%20at%20TV%20news%20or%20from%20newspaper%20columns.%20But%2C%20they%20are%20generally%20unwilling%20to%20take%20tangible%20steps%20to%20use%20the%20occasion%20of%20Christmas%20to%20protest%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%20and%20the%20colonialist-militaristic%20instruments%20that%20enforce%20it.%20How%20can%20a%20Palestinian%20wish%20his%20friend%2C%20sister%2C%20bother%2C%20or%20relative%20a%20%E2%80%98Merry%20Christmas%E2%80%99%20when%20Israel%20is%20indulging%20in%20coldblooded%20genocide%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%2018%20years%2C%202.3%20million%20people%20find%20themselves%20in%20an%20open%20air%20prison%20in%20Gaza%20confronting%20degradation%2C%20anguish%2C%20dispossession%2C%20and%20political%20oppression.%20They%20remain%20afraid%20for%20their%20lives%20not%20knowing%20when%20Israel%20will%20bombard%20their%20spaces%20and%20ruthlessly%20kill%2C%20maim%2C%20and%20mutilate%20people%20in%20thousands%20with%20impunity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20international%20community%20generally%20watches%20muted%20%E2%80%93%20indifferent%20to%20their%20plight.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20number%20of%20victims%20multiplies%20with%20each%20passing%20day.%20In%20Gaza%2C%20children%2C%20women%2C%20elderly%2C%20young%20people%20who%20dream%20of%20a%20future%20when%20they%20can%20work%20in%20decent%20jobs%2C%20lie%20sick%20and%20grievously%20injured%20by%20the%20indiscriminate%20and%20persistent%20bombings%20on%20civilian%20populations.%20The%20population%20as%20a%20whole%20is%20deliberately%20deprived%20of%20food%20and%20medicines%20by%20the%20Israeli%20blockade%20in%20Gaza.%20In%20short%2C%20Gaza%20is%20nothing%20less%20than%20a%20concentration%20camp%20and%20one%20that%20is%20comparable%20to%20the%20worst%20in%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20little%20boy%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20illustrates%20the%20shock%20and%20awe%20of%20living%20like%20this.%20He%20recites%20how%2C%20one%20morning%2C%20he%20left%20his%20home%20to%20go%20to%20the%20sea-shore%20where%20rations%20are%20distributed%20to%20refugees%2C%20homeless%20and%20the%20jobless.%20That%20morning%2C%20as%20usual%2C%20he%20was%20up%20at%205%20am%20on%20his%20way%20to%20the%20beach%20where%20food%20was%20distributed.%20It%20was%20a%20must-do%20ritual%2C%20for%20else%20his%20family%20would%20go%20hungry%20for%20the%20day.%20He%20set%20out%20to%20return%20home%20with%20a%20skip%20and%20smile%2C%20assured%20he%20had%20done%20his%20duty%20towards%20his%20old%20grandparents%2C%20his%20parents%20and%20siblings.%20Horror%20struck%20him%20when%2C%20on%20his%20way%20back%2C%20close%20to%20his%20home%2C%20he%20eye-witnessed%20the%20bombing%20of%20a%20set%20of%20flats%2C%20one%20of%20which%20was%20his%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped-300x136.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped-1024x464.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682873%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20young%20boy%20plays%20in%20the%20street%20amidst%20the%20wreckage%20of%20homes%20destroyed%20by%20airstrikes%20in%20Al%20Shati%20Refugee%20Camp%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Photo%3A%20UNICEF%2FMohammad%20Ajjour%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20just%20one%20stroke%2C%20a%20few%20hundred%20had%20instantly%20died%2C%20or%20were%20too%20seriously%20injured%20to%20recover.%20He%20found%20to%20his%20horror%20that%20his%20entire%20family%20was%20killed.%20With%20just%20one%20bombing%2C%20he%20was%20orphaned.%20He%20stares%20into%20an%20empty%20future.%20Most%20people%20in%20the%20area%2C%20and%20who%20survived%2C%20were%20not%20thinking%20of%20food%20but%20left%20wondering%20about%20a%20roof%20over%20their%20heads%2C%20burying%20the%20dead%2C%20and%20getting%20on%20with%20their%20lives%2C%20bereaved%20and%20depressed.%20Yet%20at%20the%20end%20of%20that%20strike%2C%20Israeli%20Generals%20were%20gleefully%20totalling%20up%20their%20success%20rates.%20While%20Israel%20finds%20cynical%20delight%20in%20their%20lethal%20battering%2C%20the%20trauma%20never%20ceases%20for%20the%20survivors.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EAl-Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20safe%20place%20to%20shelter%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Palestinian%20health%20ministry%20reports%20that%20as%20deadly%20Israeli%20attacks%20continue%20about%2018%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20and%2049%2C500%20wounded%20in%20Israeli%20attacks%20since%20October%207%2C%20including%C2%A0an%20estimated%20escalation%20of%20close-to%20thousand%20or%20more%20every%20day%20since%20that%20count.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHamas%20militants%20were%20accused%20of%20killing%201%2C400%20Israeli%20civilians%20when%20the%20fighting%20broke%20out%20on%20October%207.%20Truth%20tellers%20have%20revised%20those%20figures%20down%20to%201%2C147%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20contrast%20in%20numbers%20does%20not%20diminish%20the%20losses%20or%20the%20tragic%20consequences%20on%20the%20Israeli%20side%20but%20the%20way%20in%20which%20revenge%20is%20being%20wreaked%20on%20the%20Gazans%20bears%20no%20comparison.%20The%20ignorant%20assume%20that%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20October%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20war.%20Mainstream%20media%2C%20notably%20in%20the%20West%2C%20are%20getting%20the%20public%20to%20make-believe%20that%20October%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0was%20the%20original%20day%20in%20the%20Palestine-Israel%20conflict.%20The%20fact%20is%20it%20happened%20in%20the%2075%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20year%20after%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20May%2015%2C%201948%2C%20after%20Israel%20invaded%20Palestine%20and%20grabbed%20land%2C%20dispossessed%20the%20indigenous%20populations%2C%20imposed%20wars%20and%20key%20political%20raids%2C%20and%20kept%20stealing%20land%20after%20each%20occasion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20That%20catastrophe%20that%20beset%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20is%20generally%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20Nakba.%20Whereas%2C%20the%20UN%20Partition%20agreement%20awarded%20the%20Arab%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Estate%20a%20territory%20of%2011%2C100%20square%20kilometres%20or%2042%25%2C%20the%20Jewish%20state%20received%20an%20unjust%20proportion%20%E2%80%93%20a%20territory%20of%2014%2C100%20square%20kilometers%20or%2056%25.%20The%20remaining%202%25%20%E2%80%93%20comprising%20the%20cities%20of%20Jerusalem%2C%20Bethlehem%20and%20the%20adjoining%20area%20%E2%80%93%20were%20to%20become%20an%20international%20zone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20naturally%20led%20to%20wars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fefraim-halevy-says-israel-guilty-of-seriously-underestimating-hamas%5C%22%3EIsrael%20Guilty%20of%20Seriously%20Underestimating%20Hamas%3B%20War%20Could%20Last%20For%20Years%3A%20Ex-Mossad%20Head%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReclaiming%20land%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20justice%20is%20justified%20even%20under%20international%20law.%20That%20is%20what%20Hamas%20set%20out%20to%20do.%20Today%2C%20Israel%20holds%20over%2078%25%20of%20what%20was%20once%20the%20entirety%20of%20historic%20Palestine.%20Some%20of%20those%20areas%20are%20now%20virtual%20Bantustans%E2%80%99.%20As%20a%20sealed-off%20enclave%2C%20fragmented%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20occupied%20Palestinian%20territory%20(OPT)%20and%20controlled%20by%20Israel%20within%20its%20apartheid%20system%2C%20Gaza%20is%20a%20strip%20of%20land%20that%20can%20in%20many%20respects%20be%20likened%20to%20a%20Bantustan%2C%20when%20the%20indigenous%20people%20were%20shut%20off%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20population.%20The%20Separation%20Wall%20has%20created%20even%20more%20egregious%20apartheid-like%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fairly%20well%20guarded%20secret%20in%20neo-colonial%20circles%20that%20capturing%20Gaza%20is%20also%20about%20massive%20oil%20resources%20that%20the%20West%20wants%20to%20grab%20for%20its%20use.%20Israel%20plays%20the%20role%20of%20instrument%20in%20return%20for%20armaments%20to%20crush%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20Gaza%20that%20is%20under%20severe%20attack.%20Several%20cities%20and%20villages%20in%20The%20West%20Bank%20are%20also%20under%20constant%20threat%3A%20Jenin%2C%20Sheikh%20Jarrah%2C%20Nablus%2C%20Bethlehem%2C%20and%20several%20towns%20and%20cities%20places%20north%20of%20these%20areas%20with%20nightly%20attacks.%20The%20war%20is%20broadening%20and%20both%20sides%20are%20terrified%20of%20potential%20costs.%20Israel%20fears%20how%20Hamas%20is%20joined%20by%20Hezbollah%20and%20other%20resistance%20groups%2C%20even%20countries%20opposed%20to%20Israel%2C%20in%20the%20region.%20Yemen%20has%20hindered%20ships%20from%20and%20to%20Israel%20from%20using%20waters%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20costing%20Israel%20millions%20more%20to%20transport%20their%20goods.%20The%20need%20for%20a%20just%20and%20lasting%20peace%20is%20urgent%20because%20if%20the%20war%20to%20spread%2C%20it%20could%20only%20harm%20the%20entire%20global%20economy%20and%20global%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29164358%2FF_xf5OOXwAAsXcb.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29164358%2FF_xf5OOXwAAsXcb.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29164358%2FF_xf5OOXwAAsXcb-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29164358%2FF_xf5OOXwAAsXcb-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686953%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDestroyed%20buildings%20in%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40UNRWA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20time%20to%20celebrate%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20what%20should%20Christmas%202023%20resemble%20for%20Christians%20and%20their%20churches%20in%20this%20context%3F%20The%20churches%20in%20Palestine%20are%20setting%20the%20tone.%20Christmas%20celebrations%20in%20Bethlehem%20have%20been%20cancelled.%20The%20Heads%20of%20Churches%20in%20The%20Holy%20Land%20have%20declared%20that%20there%20cannot%20be%20celebrations%20for%20as%20long%20as%20the%20Israeli%20genocide%20of%20Palestinians%20is%20on.%20They%20now%20have%20to%20pick%20Christ%20from%20the%20rubble%20of%20the%20shattered%20homes%2C%20schools%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20other%20buildings%20that%20house%20vital%20project%20services.%20The%20Churches%20have%20asked%20that%20people%20stay%20in%20silence%20and%20pray%20for%20the%20victims%20and%20for%20peace.%20This%20should%20be%20a%20mandate%20for%20churches%20all%20over%20the%20world.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristians%20are%20now%20passing%20through%20the%20season%20of%20Advent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EAdvent%20is%20a%20season%20observed%20in%20most%20Christian%20denominations%20as%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20time%20of%20expectant%20waiting%20and%20preparation%20for%20both%20the%20celebration%20of%20the%20Nativity%20of%20Christ%20at%20Christmas%20and%20the%20return%20of%20Christ%20at%20the%20Second%20Coming%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAdvent%20is%20the%20time%20to%20recall%20how%20god%20embraced%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20of%20people%20%E2%80%93%20the%20vulnerable%2C%20voiceless%2C%20poor%2C%20homeless%2C%20the%20marginalised%2C%20and%20the%20forgotten.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristmas%202023%20is%20hardly%20the%20time%20to%20be%20celebrating%20when%20people%20in%20the%20entire%20Holy%20Land%20are%20suffering%20severe%20oppression.%20A%20relay%20of%20funerals%20is%20what%20one%20witnesses%20every%20day.%20If%20Christians%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20are%20planning%20celebrations%2C%20they%20must%20be%20conscious%20of%20the%20violence%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%20Just%20as%20Christ%20draws%20us%20to%20a%20journey%20where%20we%20shift%20from%20material%20celebration%20to%20those%20who%20are%20trampled%20over%20by%20the%20rich%20and%20powerful%2C%20the%20homeless%20and%20uninvited%2C%20the%20bombed%20and%20isolated%2C%20Christians%20are%20called%20to%20work%20for%20%E2%80%98peace%20on%20earth%E2%80%99%2C%20and%2C%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20notably%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChrist%20himself%20was%20born%20into%20the%20world%20unsolicited%20and%20as%20a%20source%20of%20annoyance%20to%20the%20ruling%20classes%20of%20those%20times.%20After%20finding%20no%20room%20to%20give%20birth%20to%20Jesus%2C%20Joseph%20and%20Mary%20who%20had%20traversed%20miles%20and%20miles%20upon%20a%20donkey%20where%20Mary%20could%20give%20birth%20to%20her%20baby%20found%20them%20rejected%20in%20place%20after%20place.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20night%20in%20Bethlehem%20is%20lived%20out%20today%20every%20day.%20This%20is%20the%20world%20at%20its%20worst%20regardless%20of%20where%20you%20are%20%E2%80%93%20Gaza%2C%20West%20Bank%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Tribals%20of%20India%2C%20Manipur%20in%20India%20and%20to%20the%20people%20in%20the%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98forever%20wars%E2%80%99%20in%20Africa%20as%20in%20Congo%2C%20Cameroon%2C%20Ethiopia%2C%20Mozambique%2C%20Mali%2C%20Burkina%20Faso%2C%20South%20Sudan%2C%20and%20in%20Asia%20%E2%80%93%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20and%20West%20Papua.%20There%20is%20a%20colonial%20agenda%20behind%20each%20of%20these%20wars%20and%20they%20are%20about%20natural%20resources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170