ter%20and%20Poet%20Imroz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24134440%2FIMG_4010.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInderjit%20Singh%2C%20popularly%20knows%20as%20Imroz%2C%20passed%20away%20on%20December%2022%20in%20Mumbai%20at%20the%20age%20of%2097.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20does%20one%20remember%20a%20dear%20friend%20while%20bidding%20them%20their%20final%20farewell%3F%20I%20do%20not%20know%20the%20appropriate%20manner.%20Memories%20are%20haphazard%20anyway%20%E2%80%93%20they%20come%20and%20go%20at%20any%20time%2C%20without%20caring%20for%20the%20occasion%20or%20expectation.%20As%20I%20bid%20farewell%20to%20Imroz%20%3Cem%3Esaheb%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20his%20last%20day%2C%20I%20fail%20to%20find%20an%20appropriate%20way%20in%20which%20to%20remember%20him.%20Instead%20of%20tears%2C%20his%20memory%20has%20brought%20a%20smile%20on%20my%20face.%20Right%20from%20the%20day%20I%20met%20him%2C%20it%20seemed%20to%20me%20that%20Imroz%20belonged%20to%20another%20world.%20Over%20time%2C%20as%20I%20continued%20to%20meet%20him%2C%20this%20feeling%20got%20amplified%20as%20I%20listened%20to%20him%2C%20got%20to%20know%20him%20and%20understood%20the%20depth%20of%20his%20advice.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20was%20a%20world%20where%20one%20could%20truly%20dwell%20in%20love%2C%20be%20filled%20with%20it%2C%20spread%20it%2C%20plant%20it%20like%20flowers%20in%20pots%2C%20make%20it%20one%E2%80%99s%20identity%2C%20becoming%20nothing%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20it%2C%20bear%20insults%20and%20accusations%20in%20the%20name%20of%20love%20but%20never%20%E2%80%93%20for%20any%20reason%20or%20in%20any%20situation%20%E2%80%93%20give%20up%20on%20love.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20world%20knows%20and%20remembers%20him%20only%20as%20novelist%20Amrita%20Pritam%E2%80%99s%20partner%2C%20but%20not%20many%20people%20remember%20that%20Imroz%20was%20an%20artist%20himself.%20He%20was%20a%20painter%20and%20could%20do%20magic%20with%20his%20brush%20which%20made%20people%20feel%20a%20beautiful%20connection%20with%20words.%20His%20art%20was%20also%20the%20reason%20he%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20Amrita%20Pritam.%20Amrita%20met%20him%20for%20the%20first%20time%20regarding%20the%20cover%20of%20one%20of%20her%20books.%20Amrita%2C%20who%20had%20already%20carved%20a%20niche%20for%20herself%20in%20literature%20by%20that%20time%2C%20saw%20something%20in%20Imroz%E2%80%99s%20paintings%C2%A0%20that%20she%20believed%20could%20enhance%20the%20beauty%20of%20her%20words%20even%20further.%20And%20when%20they%20did%20meet%2C%20such%20was%20there%20companionship%20that%20only%20death%20could%20part%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24135354%2FEDPEbfPU8AEgIE8.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24135354%2FEDPEbfPU8AEgIE8.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24135354%2FEDPEbfPU8AEgIE8-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24135354%2FEDPEbfPU8AEgIE8-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-690549%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImroz%20and%20Amrita%20Pritam.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40AkshitaNagpal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELove%20is%20like%20an%20inescapable%20fragrance%20whose%20absence%20makes%20it%20difficult%20even%20to%20breathe.%20Amrita%20yearned%20for%20it%20despite%20being%20in%20a%20matrimonial%20relationship.%20Even%20Sahir%E2%80%99s%20love%20could%20not%20fill%20the%20void%20completely%20for%20Amrita.%20But%20after%20meeting%20Imroz%2C%20her%20thirst%20for%20love%20perhaps%20found%20an%20ocean%20in%20which%20she%20immersed%20herself.%20She%20became%20the%20ocean%20for%20when%20the%20river%20reaches%20its%20destination%2C%20no%20trace%20of%20it%20remains.%20Only%20the%20ocean%20remains.%20But%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Amrita%20and%20Imroz%2C%20it%20was%20Imroz%20who%20erased%20himself%20not%20Amrita.%20The%20silence%20with%20which%20he%20stayed%20in%20Amrita%E2%80%99s%20life%20proved%20that%20love%20does%20not%20always%20assert%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20met%20Imroz%20sahab%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20reason%20was%20Amrita%20Pritam%E2%80%99s%20house.%20I%20used%20to%20be%20a%20senior%20sub-editor%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGrihalakshmi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20magazine%20at%20the%20time.%20We%20were%20planning%20an%20interior%20special%20for%20our%20magazine%20for%20that%20issue%20and%20I%20suggested%20to%20cover%20homes%20of%20writers%20and%20poets%20along%20with%20celebrities%20from%20other%20fields%20to%20find%20out%20about%20the%20doors%20and%20walls%20from%20where%20so%20many%20beautiful%20thoughts%20emerge.%20When%20I%20reached%20there%2C%20Imroz%20sahab%20opened%20the%20door.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDoes%20love%20make%20people%20so%20beautiful%20%E2%80%93%20I%20thought.%20He%20was%20standing%20there%20smiling%20and%20holding%20the%20door%20open.%20A%20strand%20of%20his%20hair%20was%20hanging%20on%20his%20forehead%20and%20looking%20at%20him%20%E2%80%93%20a%20stranger%20for%20me%20then%20%E2%80%93%20it%20seemed%20as%20if%20I%20was%20meeting%20a%20friend%20after%20a%20long%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20photographer%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20had%20accompanied%20me.%20As%20soon%20as%20he%20arrived%2C%20he%20got%20busy%20clicking%20photographs%20while%20I%20could%20not%20help%20but%20glance%20at%20Imroz%20sahab%20again%20and%20again.%20I%20was%20talking%20to%20him%20but%20did%20not%20know%20what%20was%20going%20on%20in%20my%20mind.%20I%20used%20to%20think%20that%20the%20person%20who%20loved%20Amrita%20in%20silence%20would%20be%20someone%20silent%20in%20nature%2C%20but%20here%20was%20a%20person%20chirping%20and%20smiling%20with%20eyes%20that%20spoke%20even%20more%20than%20he%20did.%20What%20I%20found%20most%20beautiful%20was%20his%20down-to-earth%20attitude%2C%20his%20smile%20or%20perhaps%20the%20simple%20and%20cheerful%20emotion%20of%20love%20which%20only%20a%20person%20fortunate%20enough%20can%20experience.%20Watching%20it%20come%20to%20life%20in%20front%20of%20me%20is%20what%20had%20perhaps%20touched%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20Imroz%2C%20recalling%20a%20meeting%20with%20Amrita%2C%20said%20that%20she%20came%20to%20visit%20him%20one%20day%20and%20found%20the%20door%20of%20his%20house%20locked.%20On%20hearing%20the%20knock%20Imroz%20went%20and%20opened%20the%20door%20but%20Amrita%20did%20not%20enter.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CImroz%2C%20will%20I%20have%20to%20knock%20on%20your%20door%20too%3F%E2%80%9D%20Imroz%20never%20locked%20the%20door%20of%20his%20house%20again.%20Even%20when%20he%20started%20living%20under%20the%20same%20roof%20with%20Amrita%2C%20the%20door%20of%20his%20room%20was%20always%20open.%20Amrita%20moved%20like%20the%20wind%20whenever%20and%20wherever%20she%20wanted.%20Amrita%20was%20very%20fond%20of%20tea%20%E2%80%93%20a%20habit%20which%20became%20an%20urge%20when%20she%20sat%20down%20to%20read%20and%20write.%20Love%20connects%20hearts%20of%20the%20lovers%2C%20they%20say.%20And%20so%2C%20as%20Amrita%20was%20immersed%20in%20her%20books%2C%20Imroz%20would%20get%20up%20silently%2C%20make%20tea%2C%20bring%20it%2C%20quietly%20place%20it%20on%20Amrita%E2%80%99s%20table%20and%20leave%20without%20making%20a%20sound.%20Amrita%20would%20not%20even%20look%20up%20sometimes%20and%20would%20remain%20engrossed%20in%20her%20writing.%20But%20a%20smile%20used%20to%20appear%20on%20her%20face%20%E2%80%93%20a%20smile%20any%20lover%20would%20die%20to%20get%20on%20their%20face%20too.%20Amrita%20had%20probably%20found%20this%20smile%20after%20many%20long%20nights%20full%20of%20tears.%20It%20is%20that%20smile%20which%20the%20world%20tries%20to%20snatch%20at%20every%20step.%20How%20could%20one%20not%20envy%20you%2C%20Amrita%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Famrita-pritam-at-100-political-progressive-and-a-true-pioneer%5C%22%3EAmrita%20Pritam%20at%20100%3A%20Political%2C%20Progressive%20and%20a%20True%20Pioneer%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20asked%20my%20photographer%20to%20click%20some%20of%20the%20pictures%20personally%20for%20me%2C%20from%20my%20perspective.%20When%20I%20hugged%20Imroz%20sahab%20while%20leaving%2C%20he%20very%20lovingly%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20might%20be%20leaving%2C%20but%20a%20part%20of%20you%20will%20remain%20here.%20Come%20back%20whenever%20you%20are%20searching%20for%20yourself.%20Your%20face%20says%20that%20you%20feel%20lost%20and%20are%20in%20search%20for%20yourself.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20else%20could%20I%20do%20but%20stare%20at%20him%20in%20surprise%20and%20ask%20myself%20if%20love%20taught%20magic%20too%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20first%20meeting%2C%20I%20started%20visiting%20Imroz%20sahab%E2%80%99s%20house%20frequently.%20He%20was%20nothing%20but%20a%20friend%20for%20me%20but%20a%20friend%20from%20a%20fairy%20tale%20whose%20presence%20removes%20even%20the%20slightest%20shadow%20of%20sorrow%2C%20makes%20the%20world%20appear%20to%20be%20a%20beautiful%20place%20and%20leaves%20a%20longing%20to%20last.%20I%20used%20to%20give%20him%20a%20call%20before%20visiting.%20When%20I%20would%20reach%20there%2C%20we%20would%20make%20tea%20and%20%3Cem%3Erotis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%3Cem%3E%20paranthas%3C%2Fem%3E%20together%20and%20eat.%20Then%20we%20would%20wash%20the%20dishes%20too.%20Our%20conversations%20went%20on%20from%20morning%20till%20evening%20but%20never%20seemed%20to%20end.%20They%20would%20instead%20become%20the%20reason%20to%20set%20up%20the%20next%20meeting.%20By%20then%20Amrita%20had%20passed%20away.%20But%20Imroz%20sahab%20never%20spoke%20of%20her%20in%20the%20past%20tense%20which%20is%20why%20I%20always%20felt%20that%20she%20was%20present%20with%20us%20in%20every%20meeting.%20And%20I%20felt%20as%20if%20whenever%20Imroz%20sahab%20turned%20silent%2C%20it%20was%20Amrita%20saying%20something%20to%20me.%20We%20would%20often%20sit%20near%20the%20flower%20pots%20on%20the%20terrace%20Imroz%20Sahab%20had%20planted.%20He%20used%20to%20feed%20the%20pigeons%20daily%20and%20spoke%20to%20them%20in%20the%20same%20way%20as%20he%20used%20to%20speak%20to%20me.%20They%20seemed%20to%20have%20long%20conversations%20and%20interestingly%20it%20appeared%20as%20if%20they%20understood%20each%20other%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20often%20asked%20Imroz%20sahab%20if%20it%20ever%20made%20him%20feel%20bad%20that%20whoever%20visited%20them%2C%20came%20to%20meet%20Amrita%20and%20sometimes%20did%20not%20even%20recognise%20him.%20To%20this%20he%20would%20reply%2C%20%E2%80%9COnly%20Amrita%20lives%20here.%20I%20am%20also%20Amrita.%20Do%20I%20look%20like%20someone%20else%20to%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%20It%20left%20me%20spellbound.%20This%20is%20how%20one%20becomes%20one%20with%20the%20beloved%20%E2%80%93%20I%20witnessed%20then.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Amrita%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20Imroz%20also%20started%20writing%20poems.%20He%20used%20to%20write%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGurmukhi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20When%20I%20would%20pay%20a%20visit%2C%20he%20would%20read%20out%20his%20poems%20and%20I%20would%20write%20them%20in%20Hindi.%20Once%2C%20he%20received%20some%20cash%20along%20with%20an%20award%20with%20which%20he%20bought%20a%20lot%20of%20plants%20and%20a%20kurta.%20It%20was%20pale%20in%20colour.%20When%20I%20asked%20him%20why%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20choose%20a%20vibrant%20colour%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20already%20have%20so%20many%20colours%20in%20me.%20What%20will%20I%20do%20with%20the%20colours%20outside%3F%20And%20now%20Amrita%20is%20like%20an%20entire%20colour%20palette%20in%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20liked%20to%20watch%20him%20specially%20when%20he%20was%20not%20looking%20at%20me%20and%20was%20busy%20in%20his%20work.%20A%20strand%20of%20his%20hair%20often%20fell%20on%20his%20forehead.%20His%20face%20beamed%20even%20when%20he%20was%20not%20smiling.%20He%20truly%20never%20looked%20alone%20%E2%80%93%20Amrita%20always%20reflected%20on%20his%20face.%20It%20is%20perhaps%20true%20that%20when%20two%20people%20in%20love%20live%20together%2C%20they%20start%20to%20look%20alike.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20on%20my%20birthday%2C%20he%20quietly%20went%20and%20brought%20a%20cake%20for%20me%20and%20pointing%20towards%20his%20treasure%20trove%20of%20paintings%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CGo%20and%20choose%20a%20gift%20for%20yourself.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDoes%20one%20choose%20the%20gift%20oneself%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Famrita-pritam-centenary%5C%22%3EA%20Hundred%20Years%20of%20Amrita%20Pritam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20necessary%20to%20get%20into%20the%20habit%20of%20accepting%20whatever%20others%20offer%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20replied.%20%E2%80%9CMake%20space%20in%20your%20life%20for%20things%20which%20you%20want%20and%20remove%20things%20which%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20from%20every%20corner%20of%20your%20house%20and%20even%20the%20walls.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20often%20used%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20always%20come%20to%20listen%20to%20me%2C%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20narrate%20what%20you%20have%20written%3F%E2%80%9D%20To%20this%2C%20I%20would%20reply%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20come%20to%20you%20for%20solace%2C%20why%20should%20I%20bring%20noise%20with%20me%3F%E2%80%9D%20This%20was%20actually%20true.%20After%20every%20meeting%20with%20Imroz%20sahab%2C%20my%20heart%20and%20mind%20used%20to%20remain%20calm%20for%20many%20days.%20Anger%20subsided%2C%20grievances%20vanished%20and%20the%20thought%20of%20getting%20rid%20of%20the%20world%20left%20me%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20When%20such%20thoughts%20began%20bothering%20me%20again%2C%20I%20would%20again%20knock%20on%20Imroz%20sahab%E2%80%99s%20door%20%E2%80%93%20to%20a%20world%20where%20unconditional%20love%20and%20humanity%20were%20still%20alive.%20After%20hearing%20the%20same%20answer%20to%20his%20question%20every%20time%2C%20he%20once%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CDoes%20one%20find%20peace%20outside%20too%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20things%20happened%20and%20this%20series%20of%20our%20meetings%20which%20had%20gone%20on%20for%20years%20came%20to%20a%20halt%20at%20a%20place%20where%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20easy%20to%20reach%20Imroz%20sahab.%20He%20left%20the%20house%20filled%20with%20the%20fragrance%20of%20Amrita%20and%20took%20up%20residence%20at%20a%20luxurious%20flat%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Greater%20Kailash.%20Amrita%E2%80%99s%20family%20was%20with%20him%2C%20but%20Imroz%E2%80%99s%20Amrita%20was%20left%20behind%20somewhere%20in%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20house%20which%20they%20had%20built%20and%20decorated%20with%20dreams.%20Later%2C%20no%20one%20would%20even%20pick%20the%20phone%20despite%20calling%20several%20times.%20The%20place%20where%20one%20used%20to%20get%20answers%20to%20all%20the%20questions%20was%20now%20beyond%20reach.%20In%20a%20world%20where%20love%20is%20dying%20each%20day%2C%20the%20doors%20to%20the%20only%20place%20where%20love%20remained%20were%20closed%20for%20me%20and%20the%20path%20was%20lost.%20Grievances%2C%20hatred%20and%20anger%20kept%20accumulating%20in%20the%20heart%2C%20because%20these%20are%20the%20things%20the%20world%20has%20to%20offer%20everyday%20even%20without%20asking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20past%20several%20days%2C%20I%20had%20suddenly%20begun%20remembering%20Imroz%20sahab%2C%20with%20a%20strange%20feeling%20a%20restlessness.%20There%20was%20no%20update%20available%20on%20his%20well-being.%20And%20then%2C%20I%20found%20Imroz%20sahab%20again%20but%20in%20a%20piece%20of%20news.%20Imroz%20sahab%20had%20passed%20away.%20I%20tried%20to%20call%20the%20number%20again%20as%20best%20I%20could%2C%20but%20even%20today%20there%20was%20no%20response%20from%20the%20person%20who%20had%20all%20the%20answers%20for%20me.%20Finally%2C%20defeated%2C%20I%20called%20up%20lyricist%20Gulzar%20sahab%2C%20because%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20could%20find%20out%20was%20that%20Imroz%20had%20died%20in%20Mumbai.%20If%20he%20was%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20he%20would%20definitely%20have%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20Gulzar%20sahab%2C%20I%20thought.%20He%20called%20him%20a%20%E2%80%98friend%E2%80%99.%20But%20it%20is%20a%20pity%20that%20even%20Gulzar%20sahab%20got%20the%20news%20of%20his%20passing%20from%20me%20and%20since%20then%20he%20has%20been%20anxiously%20trying%20to%20pay%20his%20last%20tribute%20to%20his%20friend%20who%20has%20now%20departed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20it%20is%20not%20necessary%20for%20everyone%20to%20achieve%20what%20they%20strive%20for.%20For%20me%2C%20Imroz%20sahab%20has%20not%20gone%20anywhere.%20I%20always%20used%20to%20seek%20advice%20from%20him%20and%20the%20impact%20his%20friendship%20will%20continue%20to%20show%20me%20the%20way%20forward.%20No%2C%20I%20can%20ask%20Imroz%20sahab%20anything%20whenever%20I%20want%20because%20he%20is%20not%20someone%20who%20would%20offer%20advice%20unless%20you%20sought%20it.%20Imroz%20does%20not%20show%20the%20way%2C%20but%20becomes%20the%20way%20himself.%20True%20love%20does%20not%20only%20live%20quietly%20but%20also%20leaves%20the%20world%20without%20a%20word.%20No%20one%20gets%20to%20know%20of%20their%20death%2C%20which%20is%20why%20one%20believes%20that%20love%20never%20dies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703408444000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24134440%2FIMG_4010.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fremembering-painter-and-poet-imroz%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world%20knows%20and%20remembers%20Imroz%20only%20as%20novelist%20Amrita%20Pritam's%20partner%2C%20but%20not%20many%20people%20remember%20that%20he%20was%20an%20artist%20himself.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fremembering-painter-and-poet-imroz%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Infosys%20loses%20mega%20contract%20as%20global%20client%20terminates%20%241.5%20billion%20deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703408024000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-04%2F13%2Ffull%2F1649873871-5587.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finfosys-loses-mega-contract-as-global-client-terminates-1-5-billion-deal-123122400320_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20BSE%20filing%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Infosys%20said%20the%20global%20company%20has%20now%20elected%20to%20terminate%20the%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20(MoU)%20and%20the%20parties%20will%20not%20be%20pursuing%20the%20master%20agreement.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finfosys-loses-mega-contract-as-global-client-terminates-1-5-billion-deal-123122400320_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%