20phone%20numbers%20were%20on%20a%20list%20of%20presumed%20Pegasus%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fproject-pegasus-list-of-names-uncovered-spyware-surveillance%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20noted%20that%20a%20company%20purportedly%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20list%20is%20Cognyte%2C%20which%20was%20spun%20out%20of%20the%20publicly%20traded%20Verint.%20Verint%20or%20Cognyte%20had%20had%20its%20stock%20dumped%20by%20Norway%E2%80%99s%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%20after%20an%20investigation%20by%20Meta%20found%20widespread%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fus-surveillance-giants-network-of-operations-has-subsidiaries-in-india-9080622%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20the%20International%20Consortium%20of%20Investigative%20Journalists%20(ICIJ)%2C%20has%20reported%20today%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%203.6%20million%20leaked%20documents%20from%20six%20Cyprus-based%20offshore%20service%20providers%2C%20that%20four%20subsidiary%20companies%20of%20Cognyte%2FVerint%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20the%2069%20worldwide%20%E2%80%93%20are%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%20the%20four%20Indian%20subsidiaries%20are%20Verint%20CES%20India%20Private%20Limited%2C%20Verint%20Cyber%20Intelligence%20Solutions%20India%20Private%20Limited%2C%20Verint%20Systems%20(India)%20Private%20Ltd%2C%20and%20Witness%20Systems%20Software%20(India)%20Private%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFollowing%20the%202021%20%E2%80%9Cspin-off%20of%20Cognyte%20globally%2C%20Cognyte%20Analytics%20India%20became%20part%20of%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20presence%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20further%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20firms%2C%20Cognyte%20Analytics%20India%20Private%20Limited%2C%20is%20listed%20as%20operating%20out%20of%20Bhikaji%20Cama%20Place.%20This%20is%20the%20office%20of%20its%20chartered%20accountants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%E2%80%99s%20representatives%20told%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Cognyte%20was%20no%20longer%20a%20part%20of%20Verint%20CES%20India%20Private%20Limited%2C%20which%20is%20in%20Aerocity%20and%20has%20a%2050-strong%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%C2%A0scrutiny%20of%20the%20balance%20sheets%20of%20these%20Indian%20subsidiaries%20showed%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Csubstantial%20share%20of%20their%20revenue%E2%80%9D%20comes%20from%20Cognyte%2FVerint%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20subsidiaries%20in%20Israel%20and%20Hong%20Kong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20during%20the%20year%20ended%20March%202021%2C%20Verint%20CES%20India%20Pvt%20Ltd%20posted%20a%20total%20revenue%20of%20Rs%20128.21%20crore%20and%20had%20a%20net%20profit%20of%20Rs%208.05%20crore.%20In%20the%20same%20year%2C%20revenue%20from%20services%20rendered%20by%20it%20to%20Verint%20Americas%20Inc%2C%20USA%20%E2%80%94%20its%20holding%20company%20and%20thus%20a%20related%20party%E2%80%94%20amounted%20to%20Rs%2060.61%20crore%2C%20just%20under%20half%20of%20its%20total%20revenue%20for%20the%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoteworthy%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20Verint%20CES%20India%20also%20had%20financial%20transactions%20with%20a%20subsidiary%20in%20Israel%2C%20called%20Cognyte%20Technologies%20Israel%20Limited.%20It%20purchased%20goods%20worth%20Rs%2021.84%20crore%20and%20tangible%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2015.96%20lakh%20from%20the%20Israel%20division.%20For%20offering%20services%20to%20the%20company%2C%20it%20earned%20Rs%203.32%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVerint%20CES%20India%20earned%20revenues%20of%20Rs%202.02%20crore%20from%20a%20Hong%20Kong%20subsidiary%2C%20Verint%20Systems%20(Asia%20Pacific)%20Ltd%2C%20HK%20for%20service%20export%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20details%20on%20year-ending%20finances%2C%20the%20report%20notes%20that%20Verint%20Systems%20(India)%20Private%20Limited%20had%20several%20run-ins%20with%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20in%20India%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalance%20sheets%20show%20that%20it%20has%20penalty%20proceedings%20in%20progress%20with%20Rs%2032%20lakh%20due%20for%20the%20year%202010-11.%20The%20most%20recent%20%E2%80%9Cdisputed%E2%80%9D%20amount%20is%20for%20the%20year%202017-18%2C%20for%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cdisallowance%20of%20expenses%E2%80%9D%20totalling%20Rs%204.8%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20is%20a%20deep%20dive%20into%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20finances%20and%20its%20changing%20name%20trails.%20It%20can%20be%20read%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fus-surveillance-giants-network-of-operations-has-subsidiaries-in-india-9080622%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703407023000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F24204013%2FIMG_4150.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fpegasus-alternative-verint-cognyte-india-subsidiaries%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Verint%20or%20Cognyte%20had%20had%20its%20stock%20dumped%20by%20Norway%E2%80%99s%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%20after%20an%20investigation%20by%20Meta%20found%20widespread%20abuse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fpegasus-alternative-verint-cognyte-india-subsidiaries%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alabama%20mother%3A%20Joy%20as%20babies%20born%20to%20mum%20with%20rare%20double%20womb%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703406721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F38E3%2Fproduction%2F_132136541_p0h1ffty.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67815276%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kelsey%20Hatcher%20has%20given%20birth%20in%20Alabama%2