liament%20for%20unruly%20behaviour.%20Ever%20since%20our%20media%20has%20been%20flooded%20by%20multiple%20narratives%20and%20videos%20supporting%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20and%20the%20expelled%20group.%20Both%20sides%20are%20using%20%E2%80%98whataboutry%E2%80%99%20to%20remind%20each%20other%20of%20their%20similar%20behaviour%20within%20the%20hallowed%20portals%20of%20the%20parliament%20and%20the%20media%20is%20obliging%20them%20with%20footage%20to%20prove%20their%20point.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20recent%20unity%20of%20misery%20and%20insult%20among%20India%E2%80%99s%20privileged%20and%20powerful%20coupled%20with%20a%20media%20split%20between%20two%20hostile%20groups%20to%20speak%20for%20each%20side%20is%20a%20new%20phenomena%20in%20a%20surreal%20time.%20And%20it%20is%20overtaking%20most%20of%20the%20available%20media%20space%20leaving%20little%20to%20no%20informed%20and%20informative%20discussion%20on%20the%20economy%20and%20climate%20change%20issues.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20major%20Bills%20became%20laws%20passed%20by%20the%20House%2C%20while%20143%20opposition%20MPs%20stood%20expelled.%20They%20were%20charged%20with%20indulging%20in%20unparliamentary%20acts%20because%20they%20were%20demanding%20that%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20give%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20serious%20security%20lapses%20that%20resulted%20in%20an%20attack%20by%20mavericks%20inside%20the%20parliament.%20While%20the%20entire%20media%20ran%20with%20this%20story%2C%20a%20gut%20wrenching%20story%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchurachandpur-manipur-kuko-zo-87-bodies%23%3A~%3Atext%3Drights-%2CIn%2520Churachandpur%252C%2520a%2520Brutal%2520and%2520Final%2520Homecoming%2520for%252087%2520People%2Cin%2520May%252C%2520eight%2520months%2520ago.%5C%22%3Ethe%20mass%20burial%20of%2087%20Kukis%20killed%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20with%20the%20youngest%20victim%20being%20a%20month-old%20baby%20%E2%80%93%20was%20relegated%20to%20the%20inside%20pages%20or%20just%20ignored.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20year%20is%20a%20coming-out%20party%20of%20sorts%20for%20Godi%20media%20that%20now%20publicly%20squabbles%20over%20a%20gas%20canister%2C%20and%20will%20black%20out%20any%20news%20that%2C%20according%20to%20their%20handlers%2C%20is%20unfit%20for%20consumption.%20Dramatic%20public%20display%20of%20outrage%20by%20the%20most%20privileged%20about%20their%20humble%20origins%20or%20their%20caste%20being%20deliberately%20maligned%20by%20harsh%20words%20is%20a%20tad%20surprising%20when%2C%20just%20yesterday%2C%20everyone%20was%20busy%20locating%20and%20consolidating%20vote%20banks%20of%20the%20poorest%20and%20most%20backward%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwho-are-our-young-andolanjeevis%5C%22%3EWho%20Are%20Our%20Young%20Andolanjeevis%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20this%20cacophony%2C%20chief%20economic%20advisor%20V.%20Anantha%20Nageswaran%20in%20a%20recent%20essay%20said%20that%20India%20is%20displaying%20a%20strange%20convergence%20between%20growth%20and%20inequality.%20And%20a%20deepening%20of%20inequalities%20without%20any%20major%20push%20backs%20has%20resulted%20in%20not%20just%20malnutrition%20and%20low%20wages%20among%20the%20larger%20sections%20but%20a%20very%20alarming%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20education%20and%20health%20care%20for%20the%20poor.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20will%20directly%20impact%20and%20reduce%20growth%20potential%20of%20India%20in%20a%20rapidly%20changing%20corporate%20demand%20for%20highly%20skilled%20labour.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStrange%20to%20hear%20the%20privileged%20complain%20about%20feeling%20miserable%20and%20persecuted%20while%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20lambs%20goes%20unnoticed.%20There%20is%20little%20in%20the%20news%20about%20an%20increasingly%20vast%20number%20of%20graduates%20being%2022%25%20of%20all%20unemployed%20in%20India.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20white%20collar%20flexi%20staff%3A%20brand%20consultants%20and%20coaches%20running%20their%20own%20gigs%20or%20partnering%20with%20someone%2C%20are%20having%20a%20ball%20like%20never%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20evolution%20of%20our%20corporate%20landscape%20(and%20that%20includes%20the%20media%20also)%20and%20work%20being%20redefined%20is%20a%20story%20hardly%20ever%20highlighted.%20Not%20loyalty%20but%20flexibility%20is%20the%20flavour%20of%20the%20season.%20Recruitment%20agency%20(CIEL%20HR)%20reports%2055%25%20of%20organizations%20surveyed%20across%20sectors%20are%20now%20engaging%20gig%20workers%20and%20companies%20have%20said%20that%20they%20are%20going%20to%20hire%20more%20gig%20workers%20who%20are%20flexible%2C%20scale%20their%20workforce%20as%20required%20in%20an%20atmosphere%20where%20project%20demands%20are%20changing%20swiftly%20and%20workloads%20keep%20fluctuating.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20fresh%20formal%20job%20creation%20has%20dipped%20to%20a%20seven-month%20low%20in%20October%20according%20to%20Employees%E2%80%99%20Provident%20Fund%20Organisation%20(EPFO)%20data%20while%20gig%20freelancers%E2%80%99%20earnings%20have%20grown%20by%20294%25%20according%20to%20gig%20platform%20Pick%20My%20Work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22school%20education%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649250%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20IT%20firms%2C%20who%20ushered%20in%20a%20media%20and%20communication%20revolution%20early%20in%20the%20century%2C%20also%20now%20prefer%20the%20gig%20industry.%20Their%20needs%20are%20changing%20ever%20since%20AI%E2%80%99s%20arrival.%20The%20last%20decade%20of%20the%2020th%20century%20saw%20designers%2C%20content%20creators%20and%20creative%20writing%20professionals%20rule%20the%20work%20space.%20But%20that%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20case.%20Staffing%20service%20CIEL%E2%80%99s%20data%20shows%20that%20top%20employers%20like%20Tata%2C%20Infosys%20and%20LTI%20Mindtree%20are%20now%20mostly%20recruiting%20freelancers%20from%20the%20gig%20industry%20that%20helps%20them%20locate%20workers%20with%20different%20skills.%20For%20enhancing%20efficiency%20and%20honing%20their%20skills%2C%20they%20need%20not%20attend%20coaching%20classes%20taught%20by%20humans.%20Superior%20guidance%20will%20be%20forthcoming%20to%20them%20from%20AI!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20is%20reminded%20of%20an%20old%20story%20about%20emperor%20Akbar%20in%20which%20the%20he%20asks%20his%20confidante%20and%20all%20weather%20man%20Birbal%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ELa%20Birbal%20koi%20aisaa%20Nar%2C%20jo%20Pir%20Bawarchi%2C%20Bhishti%2C%20Khar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(bring%20me%20a%20man%20who%20can%20be%20a%20sage%2C%20a%20chef%2C%20a%20water%20carrier%20or%20a%20donkey%20as%20per%20need)%E2%80%9D.%20The%20new%20generation%20of%20job%20seekers%20guided%20by%20AI%20will%20soon%20be%20such%20a%20multitasking%20nerd%20with%20a%20fat%20salary.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20one%20falls%20into%20that%20particular%20rabbit%20hole%20guided%20by%20a%20non%20human%20entity%2C%20one%20will%20accept%20living%20without%20privacy%2C%20and%20outside%20time.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20clocking%20off%20ever%20in%20the%20redone%20work%20space%20but%20also%20no%20gossip%20sessions%20or%20friendly%20banter%20with%20colleagues%2C%20nor%20drowning%20of%20anxieties%20in%20a%20pub%20or%20hanging%20out%20at%20the%20corner%20gym%20doing%20pilates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20writers%20will%20have%20to%20unlearn%20writing%20along%20their%20own%20whims%20and%20fancies%2C%20the%20actors%20will%20no%20longer%20act%20but%20play%20out%20the%20theme%20from%20a%20graphic%20series.%20Remember%20Batman%20and%20Archies%E2%80%99%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20painter%20need%20never%20sit%20outdoors%20to%20study%20light%20or%20form%20because%20AI%20will%20reproduce%20old%20masterpieces%20and%20more.%20It%20could%20only%20happen%20in%20this%20scenario%20that%20the%20largest%20opposition%20group%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20online%20crowd%20funding%20effort%20%E2%80%98Donate%20for%20Desh%E2%80%99%2C%20allegedly%20met%20with%20over%2020%2C000%20bot%20attacks%20and%201%2C340%20data%20theft%20attempts%20within%2048%20hours%20of%20being%20launched.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20that%20is%20needed%20to%20divert%20public%20attention%20are%20red%20herrings%20while%20over%20a%20100%20shanties%20are%20bulldozed%20in%20one%20day%20because%20suddenly%20those%20beautification%20drives%20demand%20that%20they%20be%20removed%20as%20inessential%20and%20illegal.%20Entertainment%20and%20infotainment%20is%20the%20opium%20of%20the%20people%20today.%20Some%20of%20these%20stories%20can%20make%20one%20laugh%20till%20one%20cries.%20A%20curly%20haired%20star%20talking%20of%20struggles%20as%20a%20young%20actor%20and%20persecution%20by%20political%20and%20Bollywood%20enemies.%20A%20star%20mother%20saying%20they%20used%20to%20be%20so%20poor%20that%20only%20she%20could%20fly%20first%20class%20while%20her%20children%20flew%20in%20the%20economy%20section.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20true%20that%20many%20powerful%20mortals%20today%2C%20like%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20for%20example%2C%20have%20bad%20hair%20days.%20But%20a%20profound%20misapprehension%20of%20real%20world%20among%20the%20smart%20phone%20addicted%20young%2C%20when%20whipped%20up%20cleverly%20with%20memories%20of%20a%20great%20reformer%20suffering%20unproven%20insults%20and%20abuses%2C%20can%20build%20powerful%20narratives.%20These%20help%20turn%20the%20tide%20of%20public%20sympathy%20towards%20%E2%80%98the%20wronged%20leader%E2%80%99%20like%20nothing%20else%20can.%20The%20narratives%20may%20eventually%20prove%20to%20be%20be%20toxic%20but%20in%20a%20world%20run%20by%20digits%20and%20AI%2C%20people%20will%20have%20no%20trouble%20believing%20them.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESaakhi%20is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703404300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20123532%2FIMG_2186.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fthe-choreographed-misery-of-the-powerful%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Strange%20to%20hear%20the%20privileged%20complain%20about%20feeling%20miserable%20and%20persecuted%20while%20the%20silence%20of%20those%20grappling%20with%20poverty%20and%20unemployment%20goes%20unnoticed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fthe-choreographed-misery-of-the-powerful%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Macron's%20Republic%20Day%20Visit%20Could%20Precipitate%20the%20IAF's%20Long-Deferred%20Modernisation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11202742%2FThe_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_meeting_the_President_of_France_Mr._Emmanuel_Macron_at_Elysee_Palace_in_Paris_on_June_03_2017_2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESymbolism%20remains%20an%20important%20and%20subtle%20ingredient%20in%20bilateral%20diplomatic%20and%20national%20security%20dealings%20between%20countries.%20India%20and%20France%2C%20with%20robust%2C%20longstanding%20and%20ongoing%20materiel%20commerce%2C%20are%20certainly%20no%20exception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20the%20imagery%20of%20France%E2%80%99s%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20as%20the%20chief%20guest%20at%20next%20month%E2%80%99s%20annual%20Republic%20Day%20parade%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20will%20not%20be%20entirely%20lost%20on%20many%2C%20given%20that%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20has%2C%20once%20again%2C%20fast-tracked%20its%20long%20overdue%20plans%20to%20acquire%20114%20multi-role%20fighter%20aircraft%20(MRFA)%20to%20boost%20its%20flagging%20combat%20squadrons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20the%20reciprocity%20in%20inviting%20President%20Macron%20for%20the%20January%2026%20spectacle%2C%20in%20return%20for%20making%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20the%20chief%20guest%20at%20France%E2%80%99s%20yearly%20Bastille%20Day%20parade%20in%20Paris%20in%20July%2C%20the%20prospect%20of%20India%20acquiring%20additional%20Dassault%20Rafales%20for%20the%20crucial%20MRFA%20tender%2C%20loomed%20in%20the%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20veteran%20three-star%20IAF%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20activity%20was%20all%20a%20part%20of%20%E2%80%98discreet%20signalling%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20two%20sides%20with%20regard%20to%20these%20potential%20purchases%2C%20he%20added%2C%20declining%20to%20be%20named%20for%20fear%20of%20official%20retribution%20for%20speaking%20on%20such%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20assortment%20of%20serving%20and%20retired%20IAF%20officers%2C%20security%20officials%20and%20analysts%20broadly%20agreed.%20They%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98ground%20reality%E2%80%99%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20chances%20of%20inducting%20Rafales%20under%20its%20proposed%20MRFA%20programme%20was%20high%20on%20a%20number%20of%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForemost%2C%20these%20included%20the%2036%20Rafales%20that%20the%20IAF%20had%20acquired%20in%202016%20for%20around%20%249%20billion%2C%20its%20first%20overseas%20combat%20aircraft%20procurement%20in%2023%20years%2C%20after%20the%20first%20lot%20of%20Russian%20Sukhoi%20S-30MKI%20(India)%20multi-role%20fighters%20were%20first%20imported%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20before%20their%20indigenous%20licensed%20production%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20(IN)%20had%20earlier%20this%20year%20opted%20for%2026%20Rafale-M%20(Marine)%20fighters%2C%20including%20four%20dual-seat%20trainers%2C%20for%20embarkation%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3EINS%20Vikrant%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20its%20newly%20commissioned%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20making%20it%20a%20total%20of%2062%20French%20combat%20aircraft%20in%20service%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20military%2C%20all%20of%20them%20manufactured%20by%20Dassault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20negotiations%20over%20cost%20and%20delivery%20schedules%20for%20the%20Rafale-Ms%20were%20underway%20in%20the%20government-to-government%20deal%20between%20Paris%20and%20New%20Delhi%2C%20and%20the%20deal%20was%20likely%20to%20be%20inked%20after%20a%20new%20Indian%20government%20came%20into%20office%20following%20parliamentary%20elections%20in%20early%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdding%20to%20these%2062%20Rafales%20made%20eminent%20commercial%2C%20logistical%20and%20operational%20sense%20as%20the%20support%20infrastructure%20and%20servicing%20and%20maintenance%20systems%20for%20them%20had%20already%20been%20established%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20above-mentioned%20IAF%20fighter%20pilot%20veteran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20acquiring%20tried%20and%20tested%20Rafales%20would%20also%20hasten%20fighter%20inductions%20by%20dispensing%20with%20extended%20evaluation%20and%20trials%2C%20and%20in%20turn%20would%20speedily%20boost%20the%20IAFs%20fighter%20squadrons%2C%20which%20had%20depreciated%20to%2029-30%20from%20a%20sanctioned%20strength%20of%2042%2C%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20industry%20officials%20said%20that%20acquiring%20supplementary%20Rafales%20would%20also%20streamline%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20diverse%20fighter%20catalogue%2C%20which%20presently%20features%20seven%20different%20aircraft%20types%2C%20sustaining%20all%20of%20which%20was%20not%20only%20an%20enduring%20logistical%20nightmare%20but%20also%20a%20hugely%20expensive%20affair%20for%20the%20financially%20strapped%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20Rafales%20were%20already%20in%20%E2%80%98serious%E2%80%99%20contention%20for%20the%20MRFA%20buy%2C%20which%20envisages%20importing%20a%20squadron%20of%2018%20shortlisted%20fighters%20in%20flyaway%20condition%20from%20amongst%20seven%20models%20on%20offer%20from%20overseas%20original%20equipment%20manufacturers%20(OEMs)%20who%20had%20responded%20to%20the%20IAFs%20April%202018%20request%20for%20information%20(RfI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%2096%20platforms%20would%20be%20built%20indigenously%20via%20a%20collaborative%20venture%20between%20the%20qualified%20OEM%20and%20a%20domestic%20strategic%20partner%20from%20either%20the%20private%20or%20public%20sector%2C%20with%20progressively%20enhanced%20levels%20of%20indigenisation%2C%20in%20the%20overall%20MRFA%20deal%2C%20estimated%20at%20around%20%2425%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndustry%20and%20official%20sources%20said%20the%20MRFA%20tender%20was%20expected%20imminently%2C%20and%20senior%20IAF%20officers%20estimated%20that%20the%20initial%20number%20of%20fighters%20(114)%20could%20increase%20to%20around%20200%20units%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20possible%20export%20options%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20platforms%E2%80%99%20cost%20amortisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20other%20OEMs%2C%20besides%20Dassault%2C%20who%20had%20responded%20to%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20RfI%20included%20Eurofighter%20(Typhoon)%2C%20Sweden%E2%80%99s%20Saab%20(Gripen-E)%2C%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20United%20Aircraft%20Corporation%20and%20Sukhoi%20Corporation%20(MiG-35%20%E2%80%98Fulcrum-F%E2%80%99%20and%20Su-35%E2%80%99%20Flanker-E%E2%80%99)%2C%20and%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20Boeing%20and%20Lockheed%20Martin%20(F%2FA-18%20and%20F-15EX%20and%20the%20upgraded%20F-21).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20view%20of%20the%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20IAF%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20jettisoned%20the%20evaluation%20of%20the%20two%20Russian%20fighter%20types%2C%20given%20the%20grave%20spares%20and%20components%20crisis%20it%20is%20continuing%20to%20face%20with%20regard%20to%20its%20fleet%20of%20some%2012-odd%20squadrons%20of%20around%20263%20Su-30MKIs%20and%2050-odd%20upgraded%20MiG-29M%20fighter-bombers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20at%20his%20annual%20press%20conference%20in%20October%2C%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20V.R.%20Chaudhuri%20had%20declared%20that%20the%20IAF%20planned%20on%20domestically%20upgrading%2084%20of%20its%20Su-30MKIs%20to%20%E2%80%98Super%20Sukhoi%E2%80%99%20status%20for%20Rs%2060%2C000%20crore%2C%20a%20venture%20that%20had%20earlier%20focused%20heavily%20on%20direct%20Russian%20involvement%2C%20which%20presently%20was%20questionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlternately%2C%20shortlisting%20the%20Typhoon%20would%20only%20mean%20adding%20to%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20massive%20continuing%20logistic%20challenges%2C%20whilst%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20F-18%20and%20the%20F-16%20%E2%80%93%20a%20precursor%20to%20the%20F-21%20%E2%80%93%20had%20both%20been%20rejected%20by%20it%20on%20multiple%20capability%20counts%20during%20trials%20conducted%202010%20onwards%20for%20the%20binned%20Medium%20Multi-Role%20Combat%20Aircraft%20(MMRCA)%20contract%20floated%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaab%E2%80%99s%20Gripen-E%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20a%20single-engine%20platform%2C%20and%20though%20the%20MRFA%20RfI%20had%20not%20specified%20any%20preference%20for%20single-%20or%20dual-power%20packs%2C%20the%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20intrinsic%20preference%20for%20the%20latter%20remains%20unstated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20by%20a%20process%20of%20elimination%2C%20the%20Rafale%20was%20more%20than%20favourably%20placed%20in%20the%20MRFA%20sweepstakes%2C%20due%20to%20its%20operational%20superiority%20over%20its%20competitors%20that%20has%20repeatedly%20been%20acknowledged%20by%20the%20IAF%20and%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20by%20the%20IN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20there%20was%20also%20the%20abandoned%20contractual%20template%20for%20the%20terminated%20MMRCA%20tender%20in%20which%20the%20Rafale%20had%20bested%20rivals%20Typhoon%2C%20F-16C%2FD%2C%20F%2FA-18E%2FF%2C%20MiG-35%20and%20JAS%2039%20Gripen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndustry%20officials%20said%20this%20could%20%E2%80%98easily%20be%20tweaked%E2%80%99%20to%20suit%20an%20analogous%20MRFA%20purchase%20by%20resolving%20earlier%20glitches%20that%20would%20significantly%20compress%20negotiations%2C%20which%20in%20most%20instances%20stretched%20on%20interminably%2C%20way%20beyond%20the%20officially%20prescribed%20deadlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20previous%20anomalies%20in%20the%20MMRCA%20deal%20had%20centred%20on%20insistence%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20(MoD)%20that%20Dassault%20shoulder%20eventual%20quality%20control%20responsibility%20for%20the%20108%20Rafales%20that%20were%20to%20have%20been%20licence-built%20by%20the%20state-owned%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited%20(HAL)%20in%20Bangalore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20unwarranted%20conditionality%20had%20emerged%20as%20the%20deal-breaker%20for%20the%20MMRCA%20deal%20and%20had%20led%20to%20the%20MoD%20procuring%20just%2036%20Rafales%20in%20fly-away%20condition%20many%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20geopolitically%2C%20Indian%20diplomats%2C%20security%20officials%20and%20analysts%20conceded%20it%20was%20less%20%E2%80%98arduous%E2%80%99%20conducting%20materiel%20commerce%20with%20Paris%20than%20with%20Washington%2C%20as%20the%20former%20was%20more%20flexible%20and%20pragmatic%20than%20the%20latter%2C%20especially%20with%20regard%20to%20transferring%20high-tech%20military%20knowhow%20and%20passing%20on%20source%20codes%20that%20manage%20fighter%20weapon%20and%20flight%20control%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20remained%20constrained%20by%20rigid%20export%20and%20associated%20regulations%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20and%20hidebound%20by%20personal%20political%20and%20diplomatic%20considerations%20over%20platform%20deployments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20more%20%E2%80%98relaxed%E2%80%99%20on%20all%20these%20counts%2C%20displaying%20Gallic%20%3Cem%3Esavoir%20faire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20strategically%20suited%20India%2C%20even%20if%20its%20platforms%20were%20somewhat%20dearer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20even%20though%20President%20Macron%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98replacement%E2%80%99%20chief%20guest%20at%20the%20Republic%20Day%20parade%20after%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20declined%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20invite%20due%20to%20pressing%20domestic%20compulsions%2C%20his%20attendance%20could%20eventually%20end%20up%20precipitating%20the%20IAFs%20long-deferred%20modernisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20it%20may%20well%20also%20facilitate%20multifarious%20engagements%20for%20India%20on%20a%20range%20of%20space%2C%20advanced%20technological%20spheres%2C%20environmental%20and%20nuclear-related%20issues%20with%20a%20Western%20country%20that%20had%20unconditionally%20and%20categorically%20backed%20Delhi%20after%20its%201998%20Pokhran-II%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703403247000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11202742%2FThe_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_meeting_the_President_of_France_Mr._Emmanuel_Macron_at_Elysee_Palace_in_Paris_on_June_03_2017_2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fwhy-macrons-republic-day-visit-could-precipitate-the-iafs-long-deferred-modernisation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20assortment%20of%20serving%20and%20retired%20IAF%20officers%2C%20security%20officials%20and%20analysts%20broadly%20agreed%20that%20Macron's%20visit%20was%20a%20part%20of%20%E2%80%98discreet%20signalling%E2%80%99%20by%20India%20and%20France%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20former's%20purchase%20of%20additional%20Dassault%20Rafale%20aircraft.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fwhy-macrons-republic-day-visit-could-precipitate-the-iafs-long-deferred-modernisation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fourteen%20Israeli%20soldiers%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20as%20ground%20operation%20continues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703400720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F70x70%2Fskynews-israel-gaza_6403025.jpg%3F20231224072114%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Feight-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-13037242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fourteen%20Israeli%20soldiers%20have%20been%20killed%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20the%20Israeli%20military%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1066%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Feight-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-13037242%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.amppr